(9, 'App\\Models\\Admin', 2, 'created', 'App\\Models\\News', 11, '[]', '{\"title\":\"Du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh: C\\u1ea9m nang t\\u1eeb A \\u0111\\u1ebfn Z\",\"slug\":\"du-lich-tay-ninh-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z\",\"content\":\"<p><strong>Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n di chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1eeb TP. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u0111i T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng di chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1edbi T\\u00e2y Ninh b\\u1eb1ng xe bu\\u00fdt, xe kh\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, xe m\\u00e1y ho\\u1eb7c \\u00f4t\\u00f4 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n s\\u1ebd thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n h\\u01a1n khi di chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m th\\u0103m quan. T\\u1eeb TP HCM, \\u0111i theo \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u1ed9 22 qua \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u1eadn huy\\u1ec7n C\\u1ee7 Chi (TP HCM), Tr\\u1ea3ng B\\u00e0ng (T\\u00e2y Ninh), t\\u1edbi v\\u00f2ng xoay \\u0111o\\u1ea1n ng\\u00e3 ba th\\u1ecb tr\\u1ea5n G\\u00f2 D\\u1ea7u th\\u00ec r\\u1ebd v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u1ed9 22B r\\u1ed3i th\\u1eb3ng ti\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh.<\\/p><p>N\\u1ebfu mu\\u1ed1n b\\u1eaft xe kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1eeb TP HCM \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 xu\\u1ea5t ph\\u00e1t t\\u1eeb b\\u1ebfn xe An S\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u1edf huy\\u1ec7n H\\u00f3c M\\u00f4n r\\u1ed3i mua v\\u00e9 xe kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111i T\\u00e2y Ninh c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 xe \\u0110\\u1ed3ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1edbc (028 3504 4999), gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 ch\\u1ec9 kho\\u1ea3ng 80.000 \\u2013 100.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng\\/l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t. C\\u00f2n v\\u1edbi xe bu\\u00fdt, du kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1edbi b\\u1ebfn xe ch\\u1ee3 B\\u1ebfn Th\\u00e0nh l\\u00ean xe s\\u1ed1 70-3 \\u0111i t\\u1edbi cu\\u1ed1i b\\u1ebfn l\\u00e0 M\\u1ed9c B\\u00e0i, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111i ti\\u1ebfp chuy\\u1ebfn xe s\\u1ed1 05 \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ebfn xe T\\u00e2y Ninh. T\\u1ed5ng chi ph\\u00ed cho hai tuy\\u1ebfn n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0 55.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><p><strong>\\u0110\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u01b0u tr\\u00fa t\\u1ea1i T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n \\u1edf th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 T\\u00e2y Ninh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u1eadp trung nhi\\u1ec1u \\u1edf khu v\\u1ef1c g\\u1ea7n n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c con \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0110\\u1ea1i l\\u1ed9 30\\/4, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng CMT8,\\u2026 gi\\u00e1 ph\\u00f2ng dao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eeb 100.000 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 400.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u00eam. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m c\\u1eafm tr\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en ng\\u1eafm b\\u00ecnh minh c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb y\\u00eau th\\u00edch du l\\u1ecbch b\\u1ee5i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn.<\\/p><p>\\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t, n\\u1ebfu mu\\u1ed1n ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng sang ch\\u1ea3nh \\u1edf T\\u00e2y Ninh th\\u00ec kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ivivu.com\\/khach-san-tay-ninh\\/khach-san-vinpearl-tay-ninh?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\\\"><strong>kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/a> 5 sao. T\\u1ecda l\\u1ea1c t\\u1ea1i \\u0111i\\u1ec3m giao c\\u1ee7a 3 tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng huy\\u1ebft m\\u1ea1ch ngay trung t\\u00e2m, kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh \\u0111\\u00e3 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh \\u201cn\\u00f3c nh\\u00e0\\u201d m\\u1edbi c\\u1ee7a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t&nbsp; t\\u1ea1i T\\u00e2y Ninh.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120194958_5489530111073145_9049468000254933182_n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120194958_5489530111073145_9049468000254933182_n\\\"><\\/figure><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120185230_5489530271073129_947726663658939175_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120185230_5489530271073129_947726663658939175_o\\\"><\\/figure><p>T\\u00e1i hi\\u1ec7n ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o phong c\\u00e1ch Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng, kh\\u00f4ng gian b\\u00ean trong kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh l\\u1ea5y m\\u00e0u tr\\u1eafng l\\u00e0m ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea1o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng s\\u1eafc v\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0u \\u0111en huy\\u1ec1n b\\u00ed. Ngay t\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ec1n s\\u1ea3nh sang tr\\u1ecdng, lobby bar hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ly cocktail v\\u00e0 th\\u1ee9c u\\u1ed1ng m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb\\u2026 s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m d\\u1eebng ch\\u00e2n g\\u00e2y m\\u1ebfn th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng cho du kh\\u00e1ch ngay khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120270965_5489530614406428_448069582999732935_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120270965_5489530614406428_448069582999732935_o\\\"><\\/figure><p>Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n v\\u1edbi phong c\\u00e1ch ho\\u00e0ng gia ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a tinh x\\u1ea3o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u00e0i tr\\u00ed t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9, t\\u1ea1o ra kh\\u00f4ng gian ngh\\u1ec9 tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n cho du kh\\u00e1ch.&nbsp; \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, chu\\u1ed7i d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ti\\u1ec7n \\u00edch kh\\u00e9p k\\u00edn b\\u00ean trong kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0i l\\u00f2ng cho m\\u1ed7i du kh\\u00e1ch.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120199064_5489530244406465_4349470807019733465_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120199064_5489530244406465_4349470807019733465_o\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120197581_5489530324406457_8182512914360964294_n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120197581_5489530324406457_8182512914360964294_n\\\"><\\/figure><p>T\\u1ea1i ph\\u00f2ng ngh\\u1ec9, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00f3ng t\\u1ea7m m\\u1eaft bao qu\\u00e1t tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n khung c\\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 bi\\u00ean gi\\u1edbi T\\u00e2y Ninh. T\\u1ea7m nh\\u00ecn tr\\u00ean cao \\u0111\\u1eaft gi\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u01b0a du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ea3m quan tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1.<\\/p><p><strong>CLICK THAM KH\\u1ea2O NGAY&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ivivu.com\\/khach-san-tay-ninh\\/khach-san-vinpearl-tay-ninh?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\\\"><strong>KH\\u00c1CH S\\u1ea0N VINPEARL T\\u00c2Y NINH<\\/strong><\\/a><strong>&nbsp;V\\u1edaI GI\\u00c1 \\u01afU \\u0110\\u00c3I C\\u1ef0C T\\u1ed0T<\\/strong><\\/p><p><br><strong>Nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m check-in kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua khi \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-haggg___.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu- haggg___\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @haggg___<\\/i><\\/p><p><strong>1. Nu\\u0301i Ba\\u0300 \\u0110en<\\/strong><\\/p><p>N\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en n\\u1eb1m c\\u00e1ch th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 T\\u00e2y Ninh kho\\u1ea3ng 8km, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c bi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u01b0 l\\u00e0 n\\u00f3c nh\\u00e0 c\\u1ee7a v\\u00f9ng Nam B\\u1ed9, v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ec9nh cao nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 986m, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh b\\u1edfi ba ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai: n\\u00fai Heo, n\\u00