2014/10/Du-lich-vung-tau-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z-iVIVU.com-2.jpg\" alt=\"Khu vc Bi Sau.\"></figure><p><i>Khu vc bi sau. nh: Panoramio</i></p><p><strong>Bi Trc</strong></p><p>Trung tm ca thnh ph Vng Tu nm  bi trc, ni y tp trung kh nhiu cao c v cc khu mua bn sm ut. Du khch thng chn bi tm  khu vc bi sau v bi trc  nhim hn do mt  dn c sinh sng v du khch tp trung ng c. Tuy nhin, bi trc s l ni l tng  bn ngm hong hn hoc i do.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2014/10/Du-lich-vung-tau-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z-iVIVU.com-3.jpg\" alt=\"Khu vc cng vin Bi Trc.\"></figure><p><i>Khu vc cng vin bi trc. nh: Panoramio</i></p><p><strong>Long Hi</strong></p><p>Cch thnh ph H Ch Minh khong 110km v hng ng Bc (tng ng khong 2  2,5 ting i xe my), bin Long Hi l a im ngh dng c nhiu du khch yu thch. Long Hi c bi bin p vi ln nc trong xanh, ct vng tri di v nhng khu resort gn bin. c bit, bin Long Hi c nhiu hi sn ti ngon vi gi kh r. Sui khong nng Bnh Chu nm trn tuyn ng du lch Long Hi, cng l im dng chn th v vi du khch.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2014/10/Du-lich-vung-tau-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z-iVIVU.com-4-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"o Nc Ngt Long Hi.\"></figure><p><i>o Nc Ngt Long Hi. nh: vnphoto.net</i></p><p><strong>H Cc  H Trm</strong></p><p>Hai bi bin ny u thuc huyn Xuyn Mc, l im du lch hp dn du khch bi nt hoang s nguyn thy him c.&nbsp;Bin  y nc trong xanh in y ct quanh nm, khu bi tm ct trng tri rng,  dc thoai thoi v c bit p th mng nh cc tng  nm trong bi tm to nn nhng t sng bin tung bt trng xa.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2014/10/cam-nang-du-lich-vung-tau-ivivu-51.jpg\" alt=\"nh: dulichhotram\"></figure><p><i>nh: dulichhotram</i></p><p><strong>Sui </strong></p><p>Bin Sui  nm ti x Bnh Chu, huyn Xuyn Mc, cch ch Bnh Chu khong 3km, trn ng hng v sui nc nng Bnh Chu. Bin Sui  va c sui nc ngt, va c bi ct trng mn mng vi nc bin xanh mnh mng. y l mt trong nhng bi bin him hoi  Vit Nam va c nc ngt v nc mn.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2014/10/cam-nang-du-lich-vung-tau-ivivu-6.jpg\" alt=\"nh: ST\"></figure><p><i>nh: ST</i></p><p><strong>Cn o</strong></p><p>Cn o ni ting vi bi bin trong vt, hng da xanh v b ct trng c th lm say m bt c du khch no. Tht d hiu v sao Cn o thu ht rt nhiu du khch trong v ngoi nc n thng lm. Vi v p hoang s v cha b tc ng nhiu bi ngnh cng nghip du lch, Cn o hin nay qu tht l thin ng du lch him c  Vit Nam.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/11/Du-lich-vung-tau-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z-iVIVU.com-5.jpg\" alt=\"Bi bin hoang s ca Cn o.\"></figure><p><i>Bi bin hoang s ca Cn o. nh: Airmekong.com</i></p><h2><strong>Nhng a danh khng th b qua khi du lch </strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-vung-tau?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>Vng Tu</strong></a></h2><p>Du khch vn quen chn Vng Tu  i gi dp cui tun bi v tr rt gn TP. HCM. Song ngoi nhng bi tm v qun n ngon, Vng Tu cn nhiu im du lch th v  bn khm ph.</p><p><strong>Thch Ca Pht i</strong></p><p>y l mt ngi cha nm trn sn ni Ln ca thnh ph Vng Tu. V p ca ngi cha kt hp rt kho lo gia kin trc tn gio v phong cnh thin nhin. ng ch  nht l ngn thp Bt Gic cao 19m v tng Pht Thch Ca ngi thin trn ta sen xy bn lng chng ni, du khch ng t xa c th chim ngng c.</p><p>ng i: Du khch n Thch Ca Pht i theo ng L Li, r v ng Trn Ph hoc t ng Trn Ph  bi Trc theo ng ven bin i qua bi Du, ti a phn Bn  l gp Thch Ca Pht i.</p>', 0, 'on', 6, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:40:54', '2020-11-21 00:41:24'),
(16, 'Du lch  Nng: Cm nang t A n Z', 'du-lich-da-nang-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605944551046.jpg', '<h2><strong>Gii thiu du lch  Nng</strong></h2><p>Nm  vng Nam Trung B,  Nng c c ni, ng bng v bin. Cc im tham quan du lch ni ting khi <strong>du lch  Nng</strong> bao gm khu du lch B N, bi bin M Kh, v khu vui chi gii tr trong nh Fantasy Park ln nht chu .  Nng cn c nhiu thng cnh m hn nh o Hi Vn, rng nguyn sinh  bn o Sn Tr v Ng Hnh Sn. c bit,  Nng c bao quanh bi 3 di sn vn ha th gii l Hu, Hi An v M Sn, v xa hn cht na l Vn Quc Gia Phong Nha  K Bng. Hng nm  Nng t chc L hi pho hoa thu ht rt nhiu du khch mun phng n tham d.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/da-nang-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"nh: dukdndanang\"></figure><p><i>nh: dukdndanang</i></p><h2><strong>Di chuyn: phng tin, di chuyn khi </strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-da-nang?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>du lch  Nng</strong></a></h2><p>Bt c phng tin no cng c th a bn n c  Nng. Bn cnh nhng li th v cnh quan, s thun tin di chuyn cng l mt u th ca thnh ph ny. Bn c th i my bay, xe la, xe khch, xe my,</p><p><strong>Xe la</strong>:&nbsp;i xe la&nbsp;t H Ni hoc Si Gn n  Nng mt khong 14  20 ting ty thuc vo chuyn tu chm hay nhanh. i t Si Gn th lu hn v khong cch xa hn.</p><p>Gi v t H Ni i  Nng: 300  650.000 VN ty thuc vo cc loi gh. (Bn c th&nbsp;lin h t v <a href=\"http://dsvn.vn/#/\"><strong>Ti y</strong></a>)</p><p>Gi v t Si Gn i  Nng t: 900  1.300.000 VN ty thuc vo cc loi gh.&nbsp;(Bn c th&nbsp;lin h t v <a href=\"http://dsvn.vn/#/\"><strong>Ti y</strong></a>)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>My bay</strong>: T H Ni n  Nng, gi v dao ng t 700.000 VN n 2.200.000 VN, ty hng hng khng. Mt 1 ting 30 pht  n  Nng. Tng t i vi tuyn Si Gn   Nng.&nbsp;(Bn c th&nbsp;lin h t v&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/ve-may-bay/?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>Ti y</strong></a>)</p><p><strong>Xe khch</strong>:&nbsp;Xe khch i  Nng thng l xe Bc  Nam ging nm. Gi v v cht lng khng chnh lch nhau nhiu, bn c th tham kho gi v ca cc hng: Hong Long, Mai Linh, Hlink, Thun Tho, Phng Trang, Sinh Cafe</p><p> H Ni bn c th bt xe khch i  Nng ti bn Gip Bt, bn xe Nc Ngm.</p><p> Si Gn bn mua v  bn xe Min ng.</p><p>Lu : Nn mua trc, hoc gi in trc cho nh xe  trnh tnh trng ht v. Hoc ln xe b nhi nht.</p><p>Gi v khong t 500  700 VND,&nbsp;&nbsp;thi gian 18 n 20 ting t H Ni/Si Gn n  Nng.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/du-lich-da-nang-ivivu-10.jpg\" alt=\"Pht o v khm ph thnh ph bng xe my l tri nghim rt c yu thch ti  Nng.&nbsp;nh: Glenn Phillips\"></figure><p><i>Pht o v khm ph thnh ph bng xe my l tri nghim rt c yu thch ti  Nng.&nbsp;nh: Glenn Phillips</i></p><p><strong>Ni thnh  Nng</strong>:</p><p><strong>Xe my</strong>: tin li v d dng khm ph cc im tham quan ca <i>du lch  Nng</i>. C th thu ti khch sn hay cc im thu xe my, gi t 90.000 VND  150.000VND/xe/ngy.</p><p>Mt s <i><strong>im cho thu xe my  Nng</strong></i> bn c th tham kho:</p><p> Cng ty cho thu xe my Lm Nguyn, T: 0942.35.35.35 v 0965.977.768(Gp Anh )  /c: ng H Hun Nghip  Ng Hnh sn.</p><p> Cng ty xe my Bnh Minh: 0986.86.29.86  0938.006.843 (Anh Khoa). a ch: 82 Thch Lam, Sn Tr,  Nng st bi bin M Kh.</p><p> Cng ty xe my Trng t 0969.722.744 (A. Tun) v 0969.822.844 (A. t), a ch K65/86 T Hin Thnh (rt gn khu bin M Kh), c nhn giao xe ti khch sn v sn bay.</p><p> Cng ty Anh Tun Motorbike gn sn bay  nng. a ch 143/16 Tiu La. Lin h : 0905.70.80.90 (A. Tun) hoc 0988.000.835  0988.000.875 (Hong Anh)</p><p><strong>Taxi</strong>: Mt s hng taxi ph bin ti  Nng</p><p>Taxi Mai Linh  (0511). 3.56.56.56</p><p>Taxi Hng Khng  (0511).3.27.27.27</p><p>Taxi Sng Hn  (0511).3.72.72.72</p><p>Taxi Vinasun Green  (0511).3.68.68.68</p><h2><strong>Thi tit, thi gian du lch</strong></h2><p> Nng l mt thnh ph thuc vng Nam Trung B nn c kh hu nhit i gi ma in hnh, nhit  cao v t bin ng. Mi nm c hai ma r rt: ma ma t thng 8 n thng 12 v ma 