(17, 'Du lch Hu: Cm nang t A n Z', 'du-lich-hue-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605944619457.jpg', '<p>Cng tham kho cm nang du lch Hu&nbsp;thng xuyn&nbsp;c cp nht thng tin&nbsp;mi ti&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>iVIVU.com</strong></a> nh!</p><p>Nhc n Hu ngi ta thng ngh ngay n cc cung in, n i mang hi th c xa mt thi vua cha huy hong. Ai cng mun mt ln du lch Hu  tn mt nhn thy nhng bng chng sinh ng ca triu i phong kin cui cng. Khng ch th, nt du dng th thi v cuc sng chm ri ni y cng c nhiu ngi yu thch.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-hue-ivivu-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hoa phng vng  Hu c trng dc cc con ph Ng Quyn, ng ba Phan Bi Chu, L Li. Ni y thu ht nhiu du khch, cng nh nhng ngi yu nhip nh ti  tha sc sng tc. nh: Tom Hoang\"></figure><p><i>Hoa phng vng  Hu c trng dc cc con ph Ng Quyn, ng ba Phan Bi Chu, L Li. Ni y thu ht nhiu du khch, cng nh nhng ngi yu nhip nh ti  tha sc sng tc. nh: Tom Hoang</i></p><h2><strong>Di chuyn: Phng tin, di chuyn khi du lch Hu</strong></h2><p><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/ve-may-bay/ho-chi-minh-di-hue?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>My bay</strong>:</a> Sn bay Ph Bi va m ca sau thi gian nng cp  phc v du lch Hu. Hng ngy u c chuyn bay t &nbsp;TP.HCM v H Ni n Hu vi nhiu hng nh Vietnam Airlines, VietjetAir, Jetstar gi v khong t 900.000 ng/chiu.</p><p><strong>Tu ha (Xe la)</strong>: T TP.HCM v H Ni cng c tu n Hu. Vi nhng ai d d thi gian v mun tri nghim cnh p trn ng i th nn chn phng tin ny.</p><p>Gi v t H Ni i Hu: 350&nbsp; 800.000 VN ty thuc vo cc loi gh. (Bn c th lin h t v <a href=\"http://dsvn.vn/#/\"><strong>Ti y</strong></a>)</p><p>Gi v t Si Gn i Hu&nbsp;t: 400&nbsp; 1.200.000 VN ty thuc vo cc loi gh. (Bn c th lin h t v <a href=\"http://dsvn.vn/#/\"><strong>Ti y</strong></a>)</p><p><strong>Xe khch</strong>:&nbsp;Xe khch i Hu&nbsp;thng l xe Bc  Nam ging nm. Gi v v cht lng khng chnh lch nhau nhiu, bn c th tham kho gi v ca cc hng: Hong Long, Phng Trang,&nbsp;TheSinhTourist,</p><p> H Ni bn c th bt xe khch i Hu&nbsp;ti bn Gip Bt, bn xe Nc Ngm, bn xe Lng Yn, vi gi v t 300.000 ng</p><p> Si Gn bn mua v  bn xe Min ng, vi gi v t 450.000 ng.</p><p>Lu : Nn mua trc, hoc gi in trc cho nh xe  trnh tnh trng ht v. Hoc ln xe b nhi nht.</p><p><strong>Di chuyn trong ni thnh Hu</strong>: Bn c th thu xe my  di chuyn v khm ph Hu. Gi thu t 100-150.000 ng/xe/ngy. Tham quan i Ni th nn th xch l  cm nhn ht nt mc mc, bnh d  y.</p><p><strong>Taxi:</strong> Mai Linh, Thnh Cng, Taxi Vng, Hng Giang Theo kinh nghim ca mnh th Thnh Cng l hng r nht cng cht lng i km vi s hin i. in thoi: 02343.57.57.57</p><p>Mai Linh: 02343898989</p><p>Taxi Vng: 02343.797979</p><p>Taxi Gili: 02343.828282</p><p>Taxi Hng Giang: 02343.878787</p><p><strong>Thu thuyn ngm sng Hng</strong></p><p>Ngi thuyn, lnh nh trn sng nc, thng thc ca Hu v th hoa ng, du khch mi c th thm dn nhng hng v, m sc ca Hu.&nbsp;Mun thu thuyn  i trn sng Hng kt hp nghe ca Hu bn lin h v Ban qun l bn thuyn. Gi c cn tu vo vic bn chn tuyn du lch bng thuyn no.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>Tham quan: Di tch, bi bin, im tham quan ca </strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-hue?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>du lch Hu</strong></a></h2><p><strong>TRONG THNH PH HU</strong></p><p>Trung tm thnh ph Hu tp trung rt nhiu khch sn phc v cho nhu cu tham quan v ngh dng ca du khch. Hy tn hng cm gic m mnh trong mt khng gian hin i v sang trng ti mt <a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-hue?s=50?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\">khch sn 5 sao  Hu</a> vi iVIVU.com m khng phi lo lng nhiu v chi ph lu tr. Nu n Hu  cng tc, bn cng c th d dng tm c khch sn theo tn ng  thun tin cho v tr ca mnh nh khch sn ng B Triu, <a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-hue?s=50?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal&amp;l=G%E1%BA%A7n%20Ch%E1%BB%A3%20%C4%90%C3%B4ng%20Ba&amp;p=1\">khch sn gn ch ng Ba</a>, khch sn ng Hng Vng</p><p><strong>i Ni</strong>: Hong thnh nm bn trong kinh thnh Hu l a im u tin bn nn gh qua khi du lch Hu.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sau hn 100 nm, nhng cng trnh kin trc  s  i Ni ch cn li t i chim khng y mt na con s ban u nhng vn mang trong mnh nt uy nghi ca triu nh phong kin mt thi. i Ni kh rng, bn nn dnh &nbsp;thi gian khong 1 bui hoc 1 ngy  khm ph ht.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-hue-ivivu-21.jpg\" alt=\"nh: H Thnh\"></figure><p><i>nh: H Thnh</i></p><p><strong>Nghe ca tr trn sng Hng</strong>: Dng sng Hng th mng cng l nim t ho ca du lch Hu. Bui ti, khi tri mt m, bn c th mua v, tm 50K,  ln thuyn nhn ngm kinh thnh c trong m v nghe nhng giai iu mang bn quay v qu kh hng trm nm trc.</p><p><strong>Bo tng M thut Cung nh Hu</strong>: (nm trong &nbsp;in Long An, ngi in p nht trong h thng cung in triu Nguyn) l ni trng by cc b su tp  dng c, o mo v  ng dng ca vua cha i nh Nguyn. Kin trc c gi theo li cung nh p mt.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/bang-tang-my-thuat-cung-dinh-hue-ivivu-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"nh:@huefestival.com\"></figure><p><i>nh:@huefestival.com</i></p><p><strong>KHU VC GN THNH PH HU</strong></p><p><strong>Cc lng tm</strong>: i du lch Hu khng th khng tn mt n xem cc cng trnh c xa huy hong ny. Cc lng tm ca cc i vua  &nbsp;Hu u c nt ring v nhng cu chuyn lch s th v. Tuy nhin cc lng tm thng cch xa nhau v khng nm trong trung tm thnh ph. Bn nn dnh thi gian thu taxi hoc thu xe t li (tm 300K) cho 1 tour thm quan cc lng tm nh Lng T c, Lng Minh Mng, Lng Khi nh.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/lang-khai-dinh-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"nh:@rabbjt_153\"></figure><p><i>nh:@rabbjt_153</i></p><p><strong>in Hn Chn:</strong>Cm di tch ca du lch Hu gm khong 10 cng trnh kin trc to nh khc nhau u nm lng chng sn ni Ngc Trn, hng mt ra sng Hng, n mnh di nhng tng cy. in Hn Chn c mt v tr quan trng trong i sng tm linh ca ngi dn x Hu, ngi in duy nht  Hu c s kt hp gia nghi thc cung nh v tn ngng dn gian. y cng l ni trang tr m thut t n nh cao vo cui th k 19.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/dien-hon-chen-ivivu-1.jpg\" alt=\"nh:@il_cavaliere_erran\"></figure><p><i>nh:@il_cavaliere_erran</i></p><p><strong>Cha Thin M: </strong>Danh thng khng th b qua trong hnh trnh du lch Hu. c xy dng t nhng nm 1.600 v c bo tn qua nhiu ln, cha Thin M thu ht nhiu du khch bi v nguy nga trng l nhng cng khng km phn thanh tnh, nn th.  n Cha Thin M, bn c th i  dc theo sng Hng, v cng lng mn.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/chua-thien-mu-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"nh: Thin nh Phan\"></figure><p><i>nh: Thin nh Phan</i></p><p><strong>i Vng Cnh: </strong>Nm cch thnh ph khong 7 km. T i Vng Cnh c th nhn thy c s nn th ca thnh ph Hu c bit l khu Lng tm ca cc vua Nguyn v dng sng Hng chy ngang thnh ph.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/doi-cong-canh-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"nh:@jujudemilneuf\"></figure><p><i>nh:@jujudemilneuf</i></p><p><strong>Ni Ng Bnh:&nbsp;</strong>Cng vi sng Hng, ni Ng Bnh l qu tng th hai ca to ho to nn v sn thu hu tnh ca du lch Hu. T lu, ngn ni xinh p ny cng vi sng Hng trong xanh  tr thnh biu tng ca thin nhin Hu. T trn ni c th phng tm nhn ra khp cc a danh ni ting v cnh thin nhin th mng xung quanh.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/nui-ngu-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"nh:@anhtupham8\"></figure>', 0, 'on', 10, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:43:39', '2020-11-21 00:43:39'),
(18, 'Du lch H Ni: Cm nang t A n Z', 'du-lich-ha-noi-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605944709614.jpg', '<h2><strong>Gii thiu du lch </strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-ha-noi?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>H Ni</strong></a><strong>:</strong></h2><p>Thnh ph H Ni l Th  ngn nm vn hin vi nhng di tch c xa, cuc sng yn bnh. Nu  mt ln du lch H Ni, chc chn bn khng th no qun khng kh c trng ni y, vi H Gm, H Ty, nhng qun cafe trm mc, nhng con ng nh v nhng gnh hng rong.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-ha-noi-ivivu-8.jpg\" alt=\"nh: Nguyn Cnh Tng\"></figure><p><i>nh: Nguyn Cnh Tng</i></p><h2><strong>Di chuyn: phng tin, di chuyn khi du lch H Ni</strong></h2><p><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/ve-may-bay/ho-chi-minh-di-ha-noi?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>My bay</strong>:</a> Do l th  ca c nc nn c rt nhiu chuyn bay hng ngy t cc thnh ph khc n H Ni. Bn c th tham kho gi v ca cc hng hng khng nh: Jetstar Pacific, Vietjet Air hay Vietnam Airlines.</p><p><i>Cch di chuyn t sn bay Ni Bi v trung tm thnh ph</i></p><p><i><strong>Taxi:</strong> </i> di chuyn t sn bay quc t Ni Bi n trung tm thnh ph H Ni bn c th chn taxi vi gi khong 350.000 ng  450.000 ng. Mt s cch i ghp hay cc hng taxi t nhn khc gi mi tuyn cng khong t 150.000 ng n 250.000 ng.</p><p><i><strong>Xe but:&nbsp;</strong></i>H Ni hin c 4 tuyn xe but chy tuyn trung tm thnh ph ln sn bay Ni Bi, trong  c 3 tuyn c gi v c tr gi v mt tuyn but cht lng cao.</p><p>- Xe s 7: Xut pht t bn Cu Giy, chy qua cc tuyn ng Nguyn Vn Huyn, Hong Quc Vit, Phm Vn ng, cu Thng Long, V Vn Kit,   nh ga T1 v ngc li. Xe xut pht t bn Cu Giy lc 5h sng v chuyn mun nht t sn bay Ni Bi l 22h30.</p><p>Thi gian chy mt lt khong 60 pht. Hn ch ca xe ny l dng kh nhiu bn v xe rt ng khch nn t khi c ch ngi. Gi v 8.000 ng.</p><p>- Xe s 17: Xut pht t bn Long Bin (ph Trn Nht Dut), chy qua cu Chng Dng, Nguyn Vn C, Ng Gia T, cu ung, qua ng Anh, ng ni quc l 2, V Vn Kit, V Nguyn Gip,   nh ga T1 v quay ngc li. Xe xut pht t bn Long Bin lc 5h sng v chuyn mun nht t sn bay Ni Bi l 22h.</p><p>Thi gian chy mt lt ca xe t im u n im cui khong 1 ting 45 pht. u im ca tuyn xe ny l khng ng khch nn hnh khch thng c gh ngi y . Gi v 9.000 ng.</p><p>- Xe s 90: Xut pht t s 1 Kim M, chy qua cc tuyn ng Ni Trc, Liu Giai, Thy Khu, Lc Long Qun, cu Nht Tn, V Nguyn Gip, nh ga ni a T1 (snh ga i tng 2), nh ga quc t T2, quay li bi  xe. Lch chy xe  bn Kim M t 5h30 n 21h10 v  sn bay Ni Bi l 6h40 n 22h30.</p><p>Tn sut xe chy t 20 n 30 pht/lt, thi gian 50 n 60 pht, lng hnh khch khng qu ng, ty thi im trong ngy. Gi v 9.000 ng.</p><p>- Xe s 86: Xut pht t ga H Ni, qua Nguyn Du, Trn Hng o, D Tng, L Thng Kit, Hng Bi, qua h Hon Kim, Hng Tre, im trung chuyn Long Bin, Yn Ph, Nghi Tm, u C, cu Nht Tn, V Nguyn Gip, ga ni a T1 (snh i tng 2), ga quc t T2 (snh i tng 2), cng vo bi  xe nh ga T1. Xe chy  ga H Ni (t 5h05 n 21h40),  Ni Bi (t 6h18 n 22h58).</p><p>Thi gian chy mt lt khong 60 pht, tn sut 25-30 pht/chuyn. y l tuyn but cht lng cao, c ch  hnh l ln cho hnh khch, h thng m thanh ting Vit v ting Anh, mn hnh LED hin th tuyn ng, wifi min ph. Xe khng qu ng khch, nhng cn lu  ch c 25 ch ngi. Gi v 30.000 ng.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/03/cach-di-chuyen-tiet-kiem-tu-noi-bai-ve-trung-tam-ha-noi-ivivu-2.jpg\" alt=\"Xe but chy tuyn trung tm H Ni - Ni Bi. \"></figure><p><strong>Xe ca cc hng hng khng</strong></p><p>Cc hng hng khng trong nc nh Vietnam Airlines, Jetstar hay Vietjet Air u c xe a n hnh khch t sn bay v H Ni, thng l xe loi 16 ch hoc 45 ch. K c bn khng bay ca nhng hng hng khng ny, bn vn c th i xe but ca hng. Xe thng  ngay ca sn bay  hnh khch d dng nhn thy. Bn cn hi gi c v tuyn ng trc khi i. Thng thng cc xe ny s c nhng l trnh c nh, nhng c th linh hot ty thuc vo hnh khch.</p><p>Gi ca cc xe khch ny thng l 40.000 ng/ngi. Cc xe s c im  cui trong thnh ph  s 1 ph Quang Trung, qun Hon Kim, 204 Trn Quang Khi, 69 Trn Nhn Tng (gn rp xic trung ng).</p><p><strong>Tu la</strong>: Gi v tu Thng Nht Bc Nam dao ng t 1,166,000/chiu n 1,246,000/chiu. T ga H Ni nm trn ng L Dun n trung tm thnh ph mt khong 10 n 15 pht i taxi</p><p><strong> H Ni</strong>: Mt trong nhng nt c o ca du lch H Ni l xch l ph c. Rt nhiu du khch n H Ni chn phng tin ny  tham quan, khm ph nhng nt p c knh trn tng con ph gia mt H Ni sm ut v no nhit. Nu xch l mang li nt c xa th xe in l phng tin ca du lch xanh hin i v rt mi ca du lch H Ni. Bn s c khm ph mt H Ni vn minh, lch s vi nhp sng hin i.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-ha-noi-ivivu-4.jpg\" alt=\"nh: Guu\"></figure><p><i>nh: Guu</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>a im tham quan, vui chi khi n&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-ha-noi?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>du lch H Ni</strong></a><strong>:</strong></h2><p><strong>TRUNG TM H NI</strong></p><p><strong>H Hon Kim</strong>: im c bit ca a l H Ni l trong lng thnh ph c rt nhiu h v bao quanh thnh ph l nhng con sng ln. H Hon Kim nm ngay gia trung tm thnh ph vi thp ra c knh nm trn mt bn o nh gia h. Bn cnh H Hon Kim l nhng cng trnh kin trc y n tng v l di sn ng qu ca thnh ph: thp Bt, i Nghin, cu Th Hc dn vo lu c Nguyt hay nh Trn Batrn li dn vo n Ngc Sn.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-ha-noi-ivivu-3.jpg\" alt=\"nh: Lan Chi/Kenh14\"></figure><p><i>nh: Lan Chi/Kenh14</i></p><p><strong>Cha Mt Ct:</strong> H Ni l trung tm o gio v pht gi ca Vit Nam v th trong ni thnh c rt nhiu n cha vi hng trm nm tui. Ni ting nht l ngi cha Mt Ct c kin trc hnh bng sen c th ni l c o nht Vit Nam, cng l im tham qua khng th b qua khi du lch H Ni. Ngoi ra cn c cha Trn Quc, ngi cha c knh lu i c xy dng t thi vua L Nam  (th k 6).</p><p><strong>Vn Miu  Quc T Gim:</strong> l ni th Khng T, t bia tin s v cng l trng i hc u tin ca Vit Nam. Ngy nay, Vn Miu  Quc T gim tr thnh im n ph bin ca du lch H Ni, l ni trao bng khen cho nhng hc sinh sinh vin c thnh tch xut sc. Cc s t trc mi k thi thng n y  cu may.</p><p><strong>Nh th ln H Ni:</strong>&nbsp;cng trnh kin trc tiu biu ca H Ni. Quang cnh thong ng v d chu khin ni y l im n thu ht ca gii tr H Ni cng nh nhng ngi du lch H Ni. Bui sng ngi caf va h c trng khoan khoi hng th ci thi tit se lnh ca tit tri H Ni. n ti cng t hp bn b chuyn phim bn ly tr chanh.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/ha-noi6.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch H Ni-4\"></figure><p><i>Nh th ln H Ni</i></p><p><strong>Khu ph c:</strong>&nbsp;im nhn ca du lch H Ni. H Ni 36 ph phng vi nhng ngi nh c v nhng con ph vn lu gi li c dng v ca chng t th k 19. Bn c th lang thang c ngy trn nhng con ph c, khm ph nhng ni yn bnh v gin d vn c ca H Ni. i ti ni y bn mi cm nhn c nt p ca con ngi H Ni, gn gi v thn quen.</p><p><strong>Nh ht Ln H Ni:</strong> l mt phin bn nh hn ca Opra Garnier  Paris, s 1 Trng Tin, con ph trung tm ca thnh ph. Nh ht Ln cn l ni din ra rt nhiu nhng s kin trng i ca t nc.</p><p><strong>Qung trng Ba nh  Lng Ch tch H Ch Minh</strong>: du lch H Ni th khng th b qua trung tm chnh tr ca Vit Nam vi nh Quc Hi, Ph ch tch, Qung trng Ba nh lch s ni Bc H  c tuyn ngn c lp ra i nc Cng Ha X Hi Ch Ngha Vit Nam. Lng Bc hay cn gi l Lng Ch tch H Ch Minh l ni t v lu gi thi hi ca Ngi. Lng Ch tch H Ch Minh m ca 5 ngy mt tun, vo cc bui sng th Ba, th T, th Nm, th By v Ch nht. Khch ving thm buc phi tun theo nhng yu cu nh n mc chnh t, khng em cc thit b in t ghi hnh v gi trt t trong lng.</p><p><strong>Khu di tch Ph Ch tch</strong></p><p>Pha sau Lng Ch tch H Ch Minh l mt cn nh sn khim tn, ni Ch tch H Ch Minh sng trong nhng nm 1960. Ngi nh sn mang dng dp ca mt ngi nh nng thn truyn thng, ti y cn c c mt khu vn ti tt cng nh ao c chp. Trong qun th di tch ny cn c c Ph Ch tch, c xy dng cho Thng c Php trong thi k thuc a vo u nhng nm 1900. Ta nh ny ngy nay c dng  tip cc on khch quc t quan trng v khng m ca cho cng chng vo tham quan.</p><p><strong>Cha Trn Quc:</strong> c kin trc ging nh mt bng sen ang n. Cha nm  bn o pha ng H Ty, H Ni, c xy dng t thi vua L Nam . Trong cha hin nay cn lu gi nhiu hin vt c gi tr vn ha lch s nh b tng th  Thng in, c bit l pho tng Thch Ca nhp Nit Bn. Ngi cha l im n hp dn, thu ht nhiu pht t v du khch n tham quan.</p><p><strong>H Ty</strong>: nm khng xa trung tm thnh ph, H Ty l h c din tch ln nht H Ni. Bn c th thu xe p nc hoc i du thuyn quanh H Ty. Thi im thch hp nht  bn n ni y l lc hong hn ngm mt tri ln. Bn cnh H Ty l ngi lng c Nghi Tm, ni y cn lu gi li c nhng th chi tao nh ca con ngi H Ni xa  l th chi canh cnh, bon sai. Nghi Tm cn ng mnh danh l lng hoa, c mi dp tt n xun v l ngi lng ny s trn ngp trong sc hoa ti thm. Gn khu vc H Ty cn c lng Ng X vi truyn thng c ng, lng Yn Ph vi ngh lm nhang, u l nhng a im nn gh thm khi du lch H Ni.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-ha-noi-ivivu-1.jpg\" alt=\"nh: Mo Gi\"></figure><p><i>nh: Mo Gi</i></p><p><strong>Nh ht ma ri Thng Long</strong></p><p>Ti <strong>du lch H Ni</strong>, mt trong nhng im n khng th b qua ca nhiu du khch trong nc v quc t l nh ht ma ri Thng Long, ngay gn h Hon Kim. Ri biu din trn mt nc v c iu khin bi nhng ngh nhn pha sau tm mn cnh g. Nhng tch truyn trong ri nc th hin r nt i sng, vn ha ca ngi Vit Nam, c bit c du khch nc ngoi yu thch.</p><p><strong>Bo tng Dn tc hc Vit Nam</strong></p><p>n y du khch c cho n  tham quan, nghin cu v dn tc hc t nhng s kin tn gio ti cc nghi l tng trng ca 54 dn tc Vit Nam. Bo tng hin c 3 khu vc chnh: Mt khu bao gm nh trng by, vn phng v c s nghin cu, th vin Khu th 2 l khu trng by ngoi tri v khu th 3 nhm  gii thiu vn ha cc dn tc nc ngoi, ch yu l cc dn tc  ng Nam .</p><p><strong>KHU VC XUNG QUANH </strong><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/khach-san-ha-noi?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>H NI</strong></a></p><p><strong>Lng gm Bt Trng:</strong> nm cch trung tm thnh ph H Ni 20km bn t ngn sng Hng, bn c th i xe my hoc xe bus  n c ni y. T bao i nay Bt Trng l ni sn xut gm s ni ting v cht lng ni ting khp c nc. Bn c th i lng vng quanh lng, c rt nhiu xng gm , ng quanh lng l nhng bc tng phi than c o hay nhng ngi nh c mc mc. Nu n y, bn c th i b ra gn ven sng, c mt loi phng tin c o gip bn khm ph Bt Trng  l xe tru. Trong nhng xng gm nh, bn c th t tay to ra nhng sn phm bng gm yu thch hay v ln nhng chic cc, nhng mn  lu nim bng gm  tng cho bn b, ngi thn. Gi ca mt sn phm gm c sn khong 10.000 n 30.000.</p><p><strong>Lng c ng Lm</strong>: Ngi lng Vit C vn cn gi nguyn gi tr vt th v phi vt th v cung cch sinh sng ca ngi xa. Du khch n y cn c th thng thc ba tra dn d truyn thng ti sn mt ngi nh c xa, hay nghe k chuyn, tham quan nhng bc tng ph ru. Th v nht l thu 1 chic xe p v p khp lng. y cng l ni cho ra i rt nhiu b nh cc k p.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/10/du-lich-ha-noi-ivivu-2.png\" alt=\"nh:@kieng_can\"></figure><p><i>nh:@kieng_can</i></p>', 0, 'on', 4, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:45:09', '2020-11-21 00:45:09'),
(19, 'Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z', 'du-lich-mui-ne-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605944822302.jpg', '<h2><strong>Di chuyn: phng tin, di chuyn khi du lch Mi N</strong></h2><p><strong> t</strong>: Hin ti c rt nhiu hng xe cht lng cao khai thc tuyn ng Si Gn  Phan Thit/ Mi N. Bn c th d dng tm n cc hng xe nh: Phng Trang, Mai Linh, Tm Hnh, Hong Long, Sinh Caf, Gi v dao ng t 130.000 ng n 200.000 ng (tu bn chn gh ngi hay ging nm). a s cc hng xe cht lng cao u c dch v xe trung chuyn a bn vo n tn Mi N.</p><p><strong>Tu la</strong>:  n c Phan Thit, bn cng c th chn tu la  lm phng tin di chuyn. Tuy nhin, vic hn ch ca vic di chuyn bng tu la  l tu ch dng li ti ga Phan Thit, v t y bn phi tm xe  di chuyn vo Mi N. Gi v tu dao ng t 95.000 ng n 125.000 ng.</p><p><strong> Mi N</strong>: a s cc resort khch sn u c dch v cho thu xe my.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/dulichmuine06.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>Tham quan:&nbsp;Di tch, bi bin, im tham quan ca du lch Mi N</strong></h2><p><strong> MI N:</strong></p><p><strong>Tm bin</strong>:  y c rt nhiu bi tm kh sch v p, im thu ht ca du lch Mi N.</p><p><strong>Bi  Hn Rm:</strong> Ni phong cnh hu tnh nm trong khu phc hp bi tm ca Hn Rm. Ni y c sc hp dn k l bi c rt nhiu tng  c hnh th k l nm i din vi bin. iu c bit l ma ma, c ngn ni c bao ph bi mu xanh r ca thin nhin. Ma nng, c vng a ma ca nng, ng t xa nhn li ging nh mt  rm khng l nn dn chi li gi y l Hn Rm.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/dulichmuine10.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p><i>Sui Tin</i></p><p><strong>Sui Tin</strong>: &nbsp;Khu vc c khch du lch Mi N u i t tn l Bng lai tin cnh. Sui Tin l mt khe nc nh nm bn cnh Hn Rm, y l sui i b vi thung lng ct rt p. Bn cnh sui l nhng i nh  t nhin c mu  v trng. Do s bo mn ca thi gian nn to ra nhng nh  c hnh th k l t nhin.</p><p><strong>i ct vng:&nbsp;</strong>Cn c tn gi l i ct bay tri di nhiu cy s t Bnh Thun n Ninh Thun. Mu sc ni y v cng l mt do mu ca m st c ha vi mu vng ca ct p v cng. y cng l ni nhiu bc nh t gii thng ln ra i. Hnh dng ca nhng tng ct lun thay i mun hnh vn trng l do s bo mn ca gi, cun i nhng lp ct mng bn trn. Hnh nh i ct vng c xem l biu tng ca du lch Mi N.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/dulichmuine03.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p><i>i ct  Mi N</i></p><p><strong>Ghnh  Mi N:</strong>&nbsp;Ni c nhiu mi  chm ra bin n sng, cnh vt rt p v hng v. Xen k gia bi  di hn cy s l bi ct nh, pha trn nh l miu B Vng, cui bi l Lng ng Thch Long thong mt, cnh vt nn th.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/vi/hotels/chau-a/viet-nam/phan-thiet/mui-ne/18911/?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>Khch sn, resort ti Mi N</strong></a>&nbsp; sang trng, lch s, tin nghi</p><p><strong>KHU VC XUNG QUANH MI N</strong></p><p><strong>Bu trng  Bu sen</strong>: Cch Hn Rm 18 km. y l hai h nc ngt thin nhin nm gia nhng i ct trng mnh mng. Bu trng cn c tn gi khc l Bu ng, n ni y bn s c chim ngng hoa sen n r xen ln gia i ct trng vo ma h. Bu sen c ten gi khc l Bu b, ni ny l bin h rng mnh mng, mt nc xanh thm c bao bc bi nhng ng ct p thun khit vi mu trng tinh anh, mn mng.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/dulichmuine01.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p><i>Bu Sen</i></p><p><strong>Thp Chm  Pshanu</strong>: Gn thnh ph Phan Thit, cch khong 7km. Nm trn i B Ni, Thp Chm cn tng i nguyn vn l mt nhm di tch cc n thp cn st li ca Vng Quc Chm Pa xa. Nhm thp ny tuy c kin trc va nh nhng c cht lc tinh hoa t kin trc v ngh thut ca ca ngi Chm. Ni y c v p v cng uy nghim v k b, l im tham quan hp dn ca du lch Mi N ni ring v du lch Bnh Thun ni chung.</p><p><strong>TRONG THNH PH PHAN THIT: </strong>Thnh ph Phan Thit cch Mi N tm 25km, vi nhiu khu tham quan gn lin vi lch s.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/mui-ne-bien.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p><strong>Bo tng H Ch Minh:&nbsp;</strong>Bo tng H Ch Minh  Chi nhnh Bnh Thun c thnh lp vo ngy 19/5/1986, y l ni Ch tch H Ch Minh   v dy hc nm 1910 trc lc Ngi vo Si Gn  ra i tm ng cu nc.</p><p><strong>Dinh Vn Thy T:&nbsp;</strong>L im n hp dn trong hnh trnh tham quan du lch Mi N / Phan Thit. Dinh Vn Thy T lu gi hng chc b sc phong ca cc i vua nh Nguyn  ban tng, trong  ring i vua Thiu Tr  c n 10 sc phong v n nay sau hn 150 nm vn c bo qun nguyn vn. C chic chung ng c vo nm Nhm Thn (1872), n nay  c 140 nm. Gn lin vi tp tc tn ngng knh trng, tn th c ng Voi ca ng dn hng trm nm qua do loi c thn thin ny thng gip , ph tr ng dn vt khi vng nguy him trn bin, trng ma c, dinh Vn Thy T l ni chn ct, lu gi hng trm b ct ng ln, nh qua hng trm nm.</p><p><strong>Lu ng Hong: </strong>Trn ng<strong>&nbsp;</strong>du lch Mi N chc chn bn s t m mun khm ph Lu ng Hong v n gn vi tn tui nh th Hn Mc T. Lu ng Hong tng l ni hn h gia Hn Mc T v Mng Cm  ngi tnh ca nh th. Nh th Hn Mc T c nhiu bi th ni v ni c phong cnh hu tnh ny.</p><p>Xem thm <a href=\"https://www.ivivu.com/vi/hotels/victoria-phan-thiet-beach-resort-spa-W364296/?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\"><strong>Victoria Phan Thit Beach Resort &amp; Spa</strong></a> GIM GI CC SC ch c ti iVIVU.com  <strong>TIT KIM HN 50%</strong></p><h2><strong>n:&nbsp;Qun n, n vt, c sn ca du lch Mi N</strong></h2><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2013/09/dulichmuine04.jpg\" alt=\"Du lch Mi N: Cm nang t A n Z\"></figure><p><i>Dng nng</i></p><p>Ngoi hi sn c trng ca vng bin, Mi N cn s hu nn m thc phong ph v hp dn. Mt s mn n khng th b qua khi i du lch Mi N c th k n:</p><p><strong>1. Bnh bt lc tm tht:</strong>&nbsp;Mn n ny  c t rt lu ti Bnh Thun, khch phng xa ti Bnh Thun thng tm thng thc cho bng c mn bnh ny bi hng v thm nng kh qun ca n.</p><p><strong>2. Bnh canh:</strong>&nbsp;L mn n n gin, b dng. C th n km vi bnh m  chm vi nc bnh canh. C nhiu kiu nh bnh canh