(6, 'J8Hz4KSDGn', 20, 'Tour Min Bc 5N4D: Si Gn - H Ni - SaPa - H Long', 'Si Gn', 'H Long', 4, 6290000, 4290000, 2290000, '<h3>H&agrave;nh Tr&igrave;nh Tri Nghim Du Lch Min Bc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Min Bc Vit Nam gm T&acirc;y Bc, &ocirc;ng Bc v&agrave; ng bng S&ocirc;ng Hng, l&agrave; c&aacute;i n&ocirc;i vn h&oacute;a lch s h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;n nm ca Vit Nam. Thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; cnh p h&ugrave;ng v, 4 m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n h thu &ocirc;ng, min Bc lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; im hn hp dn cho&nbsp;qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mun n v&agrave; t ch&acirc;n nhiu ln. Mi v&ugrave;ng, mi tnh, mi im s l&agrave; mt v&ugrave;ng vn h&oacute;a, mt di sn, mt thng cnh,...mang v p ri&ecirc;ng bit kh&aacute;c nhau, l&agrave;m cho du kh&aacute;ch ln trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nc u mun chinh phc, mun kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;. C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh th&uacute; v ngay h&ocirc;m nay!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>t o&agrave;n ri&ecirc;ng li&ecirc;n h 028 3933 8002 hoc hotline 0906 355 542  c&oacute; gi&aacute; tt.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Li&ecirc;n tuyn h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s i t bt ng n&agrave;y sang bt ng kh&aacute;c:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ct mc hu ngh&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam &ndash; Trung Quc</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-<strong>&nbsp;Bn C&aacute;t C&aacute;t - S&iacute;n Chi</strong>&nbsp;ca ngi<strong>&nbsp;H&rsquo;mong</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Chinh phc&nbsp;<strong>nh Fanxiphan -&nbsp;</strong>Nc Nh&agrave; Ca &ocirc;ng Dng<strong>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-</strong>&nbsp;Danh thng&nbsp;<strong>Tr&agrave;ng An &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>Di sn c UNESCO c&ocirc;ng nhn l&agrave; di sn vn h&oacute;a v&agrave; thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Th gii.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan Di sn thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Th gii -&nbsp;<strong>Vnh H Long</strong>.</p>', '<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 01: TP H CH&Iacute; MINH - SAPA ( N TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: 05h30 Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &oacute;n o&agrave;n ti s&acirc;n bay&nbsp;<strong>T&acirc;n Sn Nht</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave;m th tc bay i&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave; Ni</strong>&nbsp;( chuyn bay ca&nbsp;<strong>Viet Jet Air VJ 128</strong>&nbsp;l&uacute;c&nbsp;<strong>07h55</strong>). n s&acirc;n bay Ni B&agrave;i, xe khi h&agrave;nh a o&agrave;n i&nbsp;<strong>Sapa</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>o&agrave;n d&ugrave;ng cm tra ti&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;o Cai</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t do tham quan v&agrave; chp h&igrave;nh ti&nbsp;<strong>ct mc hu ngh</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam &ndash; Trung Quc</strong>,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/19/11/ivivu-cua-khau-huu-nghi.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ct mc Hu Ngh.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mua sm  lu nim v&agrave; in t ti ch<strong>&nbsp;Cc Lu L&agrave;o Cai</strong>&nbsp;( nu c&ograve;n thi gian).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/19/11/ivivu-cho-coc-leu-lao-cai.gif\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch Cc Lu L&agrave;o Cai.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &oacute; khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>Sapa</strong>&nbsp;nhn ph&ograve;ng ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n t&ocirc;i v&agrave; ngh &ecirc;m ti&nbsp;<strong>SaPa</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 02: KH&Aacute;M PH&Aacute; SAPA ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, N TI T T&Uacute;C)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: im t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng, Xe v&agrave; HDV a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n bn&nbsp;<strong>C&aacute;t C&aacute;t</strong>, bt u h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; bn l&agrave;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>bn C&aacute;t C&aacute;t - S&iacute;n Chi</strong>&nbsp;ca ngi&nbsp;<strong>H&rsquo;mong</strong>. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s c thm v&agrave; t&igrave;m hiu phong tc tp qu&aacute;n sinh hot k th&uacute;, n s n b&igrave;nh d ca nhng ngi d&acirc;n tc thiu s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/19/11/ivivu-cat-cat-sin-chai.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Bn C&aacute;t C&aacute;t - S&iacute;n Chi.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan th&aacute;c&nbsp;<strong>C&aacute;t C&aacute;t</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; nh&agrave; m&aacute;y thu in do ngi Ph&aacute;p x&acirc;y dng u th k XX, vui chi v&agrave; chp h&igrave;nh lu nim&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tham quan v&agrave; t do mua sm  lu nim, c sn ti&nbsp;<strong>Ch Sa Pa</strong>&nbsp;- ni trao i mua b&aacute;n nhiu loi h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, sn phm a phng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Nh&agrave; Th &aacute;</strong>&nbsp;- du n kin tr&uacute;c ca ngi Ph&aacute;p c&ograve;n li vn to&agrave;n nht ti&nbsp;<strong>Sa Pa</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/10/17/14/ivivu-nha-tho-da-sapa2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Nh&agrave; Th &aacute;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch mun chinh phc&nbsp;<strong>nh Fanxiphan</strong>, Cty s b tr&iacute; thi gian tham quan cho ph&ugrave; hp ( ph thu th&ecirc;m 850.000/kh&aacute;ch&nbsp; bao gm tin c&aacute;p treo + xe di chuyn ra ga c&aacute;p).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/01/02/16/ivivu-chinh-phuc-fansipan.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>nh Fanxiphan.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hoc Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tham quan c&acirc;y&nbsp;<strong>cu k&iacute;nh Rng M&acirc;y</strong>&nbsp;(ph thu th&ecirc;m chi ph&iacute; 400.000 ng/ngi ln v&agrave; 200.000 ng tr em).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: o&agrave;n t t&uacute;c n ti thng thc m thc v&ugrave;ng cao: cm lam, g&agrave; nng, thng c, ru Ng&ocirc;&hellip;ti ch &ecirc;m Sapa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 03: SAPA&nbsp; - H&Agrave; NI ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng im t&acirc;m v&agrave; tr ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn, t do tham quan v&agrave; mua sm c sn v l&agrave;m qu&agrave; cho ngi th&acirc;n ti ch Sapa, sau &oacute; xe a o&agrave;n khi h&agrave;nh v li&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;o Cai</strong>,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>o&agrave;n d&ugrave;ng cm tra ti&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;o Cai</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: Xe a o&agrave;n v li H&agrave; Ni, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tham quan:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch gh&eacute; thm&nbsp;<strong>Vn Miu - Quc T Gi&aacute;m</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Ni oc xem nh Trng i hc u ti&ecirc;n ca&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>&nbsp;vi 82 tm bia Tin s c&ograve;n lu danh s s&aacute;ch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/08/31/14/ivivu-tour-mien-bac-5n4d-ha-noi-sapa-ha-long-van-mieu-quoc-tu-giam.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Vn Miu - Quc T Gi&aacute;m.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng cm ti thng thc m thc&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave; Ni</strong>: B&aacute;nh t&ocirc;m h t&acirc;y, ch c&aacute;&hellip; nhn ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t do tham quan :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>n Ngc Sn, Cu Th&ecirc; H&uacute;c, h Ho&agrave;n Kim, Nh&agrave; H&aacute;t Ln H&agrave; Ni</strong>, Nh&agrave; Th Ln H&agrave; Ni&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/09/06/09/ivivu-tour-mien-bac-4n3d-ha-noi-ha-long-bai-dinh-trang-an-den-ngoc-son.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Cu Th&ecirc; H&uacute;c.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng khu ph m thc tr danh t&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave; Th&agrave;nh</strong>: ph Cm Ch, T Hin&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>o&agrave;n ngh &ecirc;m ti kh&aacute;ch sn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 04: H&Agrave; NI&nbsp; - KDL TR&Agrave;NG AN - CH&Ugrave;A B&Aacute;I &Iacute;NH ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng n s&aacute;ng v&agrave; tr ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn, Hng dn vi&ecirc;n a o&agrave;n xe a o&agrave;n tham quan cm di t&iacute;ch lch s Ph Ch Tch. Vi c&aacute;c qun th kin tr&uacute;c:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Qung Trng Ba &igrave;nh</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; l&agrave; mt di t&iacute;ch c bit, ni &acirc;y c&ograve;n l&agrave; ni ghi nhn nhiu du n quan trng tong lch s&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/12/09/16/ivivu-quang-truong-ba-dinh.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Qung Trng B&agrave; &igrave;nh.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bo t&agrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>H Ch&iacute; Minh</strong>&nbsp;- Nm trong khu vc c&oacute; nhiu di t&iacute;ch nh:&nbsp;<strong>Lng Ch tch H Ch&iacute; Minh</strong>, Khu di t&iacute;ch Ph ch tch, Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct... to th&agrave;nh mt qun th c&aacute;c di t&iacute;ch c bit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/12/14/16/ivivu-lang-chu-tich-ho-chi-minh.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Lng Ch tch H Ch&iacute; Minh.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Nh&agrave; S&agrave;n&nbsp;gin d nm gia th &ocirc;&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave; Ni</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; ni<strong>&nbsp;B&aacute;c H</strong>&nbsp;&atilde; sng v&agrave; l&agrave;m vic l&acirc;u nht trong cuc i hot ng c&aacute;ch mng ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct (Ch&ugrave;a Mt)</strong>&nbsp;- ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a c&oacute; kin tr&uacute;c c &aacute;o, ch c&oacute; 1 gian dng tr&ecirc;n 1 ct &aacute; nm gia l&ograve;ng h Linh Chiu&hellip;..</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/02/21/16/ivivu-tour-ha-noi-city-tour-chua-mot-cot-1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tip tc h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh, o&agrave;n khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>Ninh B&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</strong>n&nbsp;<strong>Ninh B&igrave;nh</strong>&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch cu l pht ti&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a B&aacute;i &iacute;nh</strong>&nbsp;(kh&ocirc;ng bao gm xe in a &oacute;n l&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;a ), ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a ln nht Vit Nam vi 500 pho tng La H&aacute;n, tng pht ng ln nht&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>&nbsp;cao 10m nng 100 tn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/09/13/16/ivivu-tour-mien-bac-4n3d-ha-noi-suoi-giang-tu-le-mu-cang-chai-chua-bai-dinh.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch&ugrave;a B&aacute;i &iacute;nh.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&ugrave;ng cm tra vi c sn Cm Ch&aacute;y- D&ecirc; n&uacute;i ca&nbsp;<strong>Ninh B&igrave;nh</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tham Qun th&nbsp;<strong>Danh thng Tr&agrave;ng An</strong>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<strong>Di sn c UNESCO</strong>&nbsp;c&ocirc;ng nhn l&agrave; di sn vn h&oacute;a v&agrave; thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Th gii, gi&uacute;p cho&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>&nbsp;ln du lt v&agrave;o danh s&aacute;ch 30 di sn hn hp&nbsp;<strong>Th Gii</strong>. L&ecirc;n thuyn xu&ocirc;i d&ograve;ng S&agrave;o kh&ecirc; un ln gia c&aacute;nh ng l&uacute;a, ni nhng di &aacute; v&ocirc;i, thung lng v&agrave; nhng s&ocirc;ng ng&ograve;i an xen to n&ecirc;n mt kh&ocirc;ng gian huyn o, k b&iacute; , qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch i &ograve; tham Hang s&aacute;ng , Hang ti , Hang nu ru&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/09/25/11/ivivu-trang-an.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Danh thng Tr&agrave;ng An.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ri&nbsp;<strong>Ninh B&igrave;nh</strong>, theo Quc l 10 i H Long, tr&ecirc;n ng i Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s c cm nhn, kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; cuc sng, phong cnh c trng ca<strong>&nbsp;ng Bng Bc B</strong>&nbsp;vi cnh l&agrave;ng qu&ecirc; thanh b&igrave;nh qua c&aacute;c tnh&nbsp;<strong>Nam nh, Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh, Hi Ph&ograve;ng</strong>. n&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>, nhn ph&ograve;ng, ngh ngi, n ti ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t do do chi C&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Ho&agrave;ng Gia dc bin&nbsp;<strong>B&atilde;i Ch&aacute;y</strong>, i mua sm h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a ti khu&nbsp;<strong>Ch &ecirc;m H Long</strong>&nbsp;sm ut vi c&aacute;c sn phm c trng&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>, l&ecirc;n cu&nbsp;<strong>B&atilde;i Ch&aacute;y</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; c&acirc;y cu d&acirc;y vng d&agrave;i nht&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>&nbsp;ngm&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>&nbsp;v &ecirc;m.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 05: H LONG &ndash; HI DNG &ndash; S&Acirc;N BAY NI B&Agrave;I ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, N TI NH TI S&Acirc;N BAY)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n s&aacute;ng v&agrave; tr ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn, o&agrave;n n bn thuyn&nbsp;<strong>Tun Ch&acirc;u</strong>&nbsp;bt u h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh tham quan Di sn thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Th gii ti&nbsp;<strong>Vit Nam</strong>, vi c&aacute;c danh thng ni ting:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tham&nbsp;<strong>ng Thi&ecirc;n Cung</strong>, ngm cnh&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;ng Ch&agrave;i, h&ograve;n m, h&ograve;n R&ugrave;a, h&ograve;n nh Hng, h&ograve;n Ch&oacute; &aacute;, h&ograve;n G&agrave; Chi</strong>&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/19/11/ivivu-hon-trong-mai.gif\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>H&ograve;n G&agrave; Chi.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: T&agrave;u v cp bn, xe a o&agrave;n khi h&agrave;nh v li&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave; Ni</strong>, tr&ecirc;n ng o&agrave;n dng ch&acirc;n tham quan v&agrave; mua sm c sn b&aacute;nh u xanh ti&nbsp;<strong>Hi Dng</strong>. V ti Ni B&agrave;i, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng ba ti (n nh ti s&acirc;n bay). Hng dn vi&ecirc;n l&agrave;m th tc cho o&agrave;n &aacute;p chuyn bay ca&nbsp;<strong>VJ173</strong>&nbsp;bay v li&nbsp;<strong>Tp HCM</strong>&nbsp;l&uacute;c 20h45, chia tay o&agrave;n v&agrave; kt th&uacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Min Bc</strong>.</p>', '<p>- Trong nhng trng hp bt kh kh&aacute;ng nh: khng b, bo ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, l lt. dch bnh&hellip; Tu theo t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thc t v&agrave; s thun tin, an to&agrave;n ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng,&nbsp;c&ocirc;ng ty&nbsp;s ch ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s thay i nh sau: hu hoc thay th bng mt chng tr&igrave;nh mi vi chi ph&iacute; tng ng chng tr&igrave;nh tham quan trc &oacute;. Trong trng hp chng tr&igrave;nh mi c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh th&igrave; Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s thanh to&aacute;n khon ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;y. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, mi b&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhim c gng ti a, gi&uacute;p  b&ecirc;n b thit hi nhm gim thiu c&aacute;c tn tht g&acirc;y ra v&igrave; l&yacute; do bt kh kh&aacute;ng.&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ng k&iacute; tour, x&aacute;c nhn s ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c v h, t&ecirc;n (&uacute;ng tng k&yacute; t ghi trong h chiu hoc CMND), ng&agrave;y-th&aacute;ng-nm sinh.. ca h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch theo y&ecirc;u cu ca h&atilde;ng vn chuyn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Do c im a h&igrave;nh, ti Sapa qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ch yu i b  tham quan, v&igrave; th qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng la chn trang phc ph&ugrave; hp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n 70 tui hoc ph n c&oacute; Thai di 06 Th&aacute;ng (V&igrave; l&yacute; do sc khe ca Thai ph, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t chi cung cp dch v tour cho Ph n mang thai tr&ecirc;n 06 th&aacute;ng) khi i phi c&oacute; giy x&aacute;c nhn m bo sc khe ca Bnh vin cp Qun/ Huyn tr l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Khi i du lch Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch di 14 tui mang theo giy khai sinh bn ch&iacute;nh hoc h chiu c&ograve;n hn, Tr&ecirc;n&nbsp; 14 tui phi em theo giy CMND, H Chiu, CCCD bn ch&iacute;nh, h&igrave;nh nh r&otilde;, c&ograve;n hn s dng trong v&ograve;ng 15 nm k t ng&agrave;y cp hoc H Chiu c&ograve;n hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ri&ecirc;ng kh&aacute;ch Vit Kiu phi mang theo H Chiu hoc th xanh k&egrave;m theo Visa v&agrave; giy t&aacute;i xut nhp Vit Nam l&agrave;m th tc l&ecirc;n m&aacute;y bay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&agrave;nh l&yacute; s&aacute;ch tay: Ti a 07 k&yacute; x&aacute;ch tay /kh&aacute;ch, kh&ocirc;ng  c&aacute;c vt dng sc nhn, cht d ch&aacute;y .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&agrave;nh l&yacute; k&yacute; gi: ti a 20kg /kh&aacute;ch, kh&ocirc;ng  m&aacute;y chp nh, m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch tay, t trang, tin bc c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr v&agrave;o h&agrave;nh l&yacute; k&yacute; gi.</p>', 5, '19:50:00', '2021-11-30', '2021-11-04', ' t', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605945168314.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:52:48', '2020-11-21 00:52:48'),
(7, 'hbaz6YXxvE', 20, 'Tour Min Bc 4N3D: HCM - H Long - Ninh Bnh - Sapa - H Ni', 'H Ch Minh', 'H Ni', 4, 7390000, 4390000, 2390000, '<h3>Tri Nam Thng Nh t Thng Long</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>X Bc, Min Bc &ndash; v&ugrave;ng t khai c ca c&aacute;c Vng triu Vit, ni nh &ocirc; ca hu ht c&aacute;c triu i phong kin Vit Nam ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy ni &acirc;y c xem nh l&agrave; t kinh &ocirc; ng&agrave;n nm vn hin vi mt b d&agrave;y vn h&oacute;a, lch s s&acirc;u sc v&agrave; a dng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, khi n &acirc;y, Du kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng ch c tham quan nhng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh vn h&oacute;a - lch s c k&iacute;nh nh: n H&ugrave;ng, Vn Miu, Ho&agrave;ng th&agrave;nh Thng Long, C &ocirc; Hoa L, Ch&ugrave;a B&aacute;i &iacute;nh&hellip;, tri nghim nhng n&eacute;t vn h&oacute;a c sc ca t kinh &ocirc; nh&nbsp;: ngon cnh 36 ph phng, thng thc m thc, xem m&uacute;a ri nc&hellip;; m&agrave; c&ograve;n c&oacute; th thm th&uacute; c&aacute;c thng cnh ni ting ni &acirc;y nh&nbsp;: Di sn th gii Danh thng Tr&agrave;ng An v&agrave; Vnh H Long...Ngo&agrave;i ra Du kh&aacute;ch c&ograve;n c&oacute; th h&ograve;a m&igrave;nh v&agrave;o cuc sng b&igrave;nh d nhng m bn sc ca cng ng d&acirc;n tc &iacute;t ngi v&ugrave;ng cao nh&nbsp;: Th&aacute;i, Hmong, Dao, Mng, T&agrave;y&hellip; C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; ngay h&ocirc;m nay!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ai v x Bc cng s chi&ecirc;m ngng, cm nhn c&aacute;c im y th&uacute; v:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan danh lam thng cnh min Bc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&agrave;nh hng ving ch&ugrave;a&nbsp;<strong>B&aacute;i &iacute;nh</strong>. Thng ngon danh thng&nbsp;<strong>Tr&agrave;ng An</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Du thuyn, chi&ecirc;m ngng H Long, di sn thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n th gii.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Chi&ecirc;m ngng&nbsp;<strong>Sa Pa</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; th trn trong m&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Thng thc hng v c&aacute;c m&oacute;n n min Bc.</p>', '<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 1: S&Agrave;I G&Ograve;N - HI PH&Ograve;NG - H LONG&nbsp; &nbsp;( N TRA, CHIU)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui s&aacute;ng, Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n C&ocirc;ng ty du lch s l&agrave;m th tc chuyn bay&nbsp;<strong>S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &ndash; V&acirc;n n (Qung Ninh)</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n chuyn bay VJ230 07:00 - 09:00, n ni hng dn vi&ecirc;n v&agrave; xe a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ra bn t&agrave;u, l&ecirc;n du thuyn tham quan Vnh H Long &ndash;  nht thng cnh ca Bc B.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui tra, Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch n tra tr&ecirc;n t&agrave;u v&agrave; tip tc tham quan&nbsp;<strong>ng Thi&ecirc;n Cung</strong>, i qua&nbsp;<strong>H&ograve;n Ch&oacute; &aacute;, L Hng, G&agrave; Chi</strong>. Sau &oacute; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch l&ecirc;n b v kh&aacute;ch sn nhn ph&ograve;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/06/26/09/ivivu-dong-thien-cung.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>ng Thi&ecirc;n Cung.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui ti, Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch t do i do&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>&nbsp;v &ecirc;m hoc v&agrave;o khu&nbsp;<strong>Sunworld H long</strong>, i c&aacute;p treo N Ho&agrave;ng ngm&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>&nbsp;- l&ecirc;n V&ograve;ng xoay Mt Tri cao 215m, vn Nht&hellip; ( chi ph&iacute; t t&uacute;c).&nbsp; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ngh &ecirc;m ti&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 2: H LONG - NINH B&Igrave;NH - H&Agrave; NI ( N S&Aacute;NG,&nbsp;TRA, CHIU)&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui s&aacute;ng, n s&aacute;ng ti kh&aacute;ch sn, tr ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>Ninh B&igrave;nh</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tham quan ch&ugrave;a&nbsp;<strong>B&aacute;i &iacute;nh</strong>, mt ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a vi&nbsp;<strong>Sn Thy</strong>&nbsp;h&ograve;a hp, mt cnh Non Thi&ecirc;n h&ugrave;ng v.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/06/25/15/ivivu-chua-bai-dinh.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch&ugrave;a B&aacute;i &iacute;nh.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch ving v&agrave; chi&ecirc;m b&aacute;i ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a chim gi nhiu k lc nht&nbsp;<strong>&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute;</strong>&nbsp;hin nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui tra, Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch n tra v&agrave; tham quan Khu du lch sinh th&aacute;i &ndash; danh thng&nbsp;<strong>Tr&agrave;ng An</strong>&nbsp;(mt qun th n&uacute;i non, hang ng, s&ocirc;ng sui c v&iacute; nh&nbsp;<strong>H Long</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n cn).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch khi h&agrave;nh v H&agrave; Ni n ti nhn ph&ograve;ng ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui ti, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t do do Ch &ecirc;m&nbsp;<strong>Ph c</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave;o ti th 6, 7, ch nht, hoc nhng trung t&acirc;m thng mi ln nh: Royalcity, Timecity, Vincom, Tr&agrave;ng Tin Plaza&hellip;. ngh &ecirc;m ti<strong>&nbsp;H&agrave; Ni</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 3: H&Agrave; NI - L&Agrave;O CAI - SAPA&nbsp; ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, CHIU)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui s&aacute;ng, n s&aacute;ng ti kh&aacute;ch sn, tr ph&ograve;ng xe a o&agrave;n i ngang ngm nh&igrave;n lng B&aacute;c sau &oacute; khi h&agrave;nh i<strong>&nbsp;SaPa</strong>&nbsp;theo ng cao tc&nbsp;<strong>Ni B&agrave;i &ndash; L&agrave;o Cai</strong>. Tr&ecirc;n ng Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch chi&ecirc;m ngng v p h&ugrave;ng v ca n&uacute;i rng&nbsp;<strong>T&acirc;y Bc</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui tra, n th&agrave;nh ph&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;o Cai</strong>&nbsp;d&ugrave;ng cm tra v&agrave; tip tc h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh 38km s n vi Sapa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui chiu, Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch l&ecirc;n nh&nbsp;<strong>Phanxipng</strong>&nbsp;bng c&aacute;p treo ba d&acirc;y c&oacute;  ch&ecirc;nh gia ga i v&agrave; ga n ln nht th gii: 1.410 m&eacute;t v&agrave; c&aacute;p treo ba d&acirc;y d&agrave;i nht th gii: 6.292 m&eacute;t. Sau &oacute; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch l&ecirc;n nh cao 3143m (Chi ph&iacute; t t&uacute;c v&eacute; tham kho c&aacute;p treo 750.000vn/v&eacute;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/06/15/16/ivivu-fansipang.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Fansipang.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng mang theo &aacute;o lnh, m len v&igrave; tr&ecirc;n nh&nbsp;<strong>Phanxipang</strong>&nbsp;gi&oacute; lnh, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n&agrave;o b huyt &aacute;p, tim mch, bnh ng h&ocirc; hp c khuyn c&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n i).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui ti, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch i do&nbsp;<strong>Sapa</strong>&nbsp;v &ecirc;m, tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Nh&agrave; Th &aacute;</strong>, ch t&igrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>Sapa</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave;o ti th 7 v&agrave; ch nht h&agrave;ng tun, ngh &ecirc;m ti Sapa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/10/17/14/ivivu-nha-tho-da-sapa8.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Nh&agrave; Th &aacute;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 4: SAPA - NI B&Agrave;I - S&Agrave;I G&Ograve;N ( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bui s&aacute;ng, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch chinh phc nh&nbsp;<strong>H&agrave;m Rng</strong>, l&ecirc;n n&nbsp;<strong>Cng Tri</strong>, h&ograve;n Ph T, chi&ecirc;m ngng phong cnh Sapa trong sng m. Hoc bn C&aacute;t C&aacute;t ni sinh sng ca d&acirc;n tc H&rsquo;m&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/08/31/14/ivivu-tour-sapa-3n2d-lao-chai-ta-van-cat-cat-ham-rong1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>KDL H&agrave;m Rng.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tr ph&ograve;ng, tm bit&nbsp;<strong>SaPa</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xe a o&agrave;n tr li&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;o Cai, gh&eacute; ch Cc Lu</strong>&nbsp;mua sm h&agrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>Trung Quc</strong>. Tham quan chp nh ca khu H&agrave; khu<strong>&nbsp;Vit Nam &ndash; Trung Quc.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/19/11/ivivu-cho-coc-leu-lao-cai.gif\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch Cc Lu.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &oacute; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch khi h&agrave;nh tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Cao Tc L&agrave;o Cai &ndash; H&agrave; Ni</strong>&nbsp;tr v s&acirc;n bay&nbsp;<strong>Ni B&agrave;i</strong>&nbsp;khi h&agrave;nh v&nbsp;<strong>S&agrave;i G&ograve;n</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n chuyn bay VJ155 19:20 - 21:20.</p>', '<p>- Du kh&aacute;ch mang theo giy CMND hoc H chiu (Bn ch&iacute;nh), n&ecirc;n mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; gn nh, kh&ocirc;ng mang valy ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tr em phi i c&ugrave;ng cha m hoc c&oacute; giy cam kt i tour c&ugrave;ng ngi th&acirc;n, khi i phi mang theo giy khai sinh hoc h chiu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Du kh&aacute;ch t qun l&yacute; tin bc t trang trong qua tr&igrave;nh tham quan du lch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Khi ng k&yacute;, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng cung cp y  H t&ecirc;n v&agrave; nm sinh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- i vi du kh&aacute;ch l&agrave; Vit kiu, Quc t nhp cnh Vit Nam bng visa ri, vui l&ograve;ng mang theo t khai hi quan v&agrave; visa khi i tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th t c&aacute;c im tham quan trong chng tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; th thay i cho ph&ugrave; hp vi t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thc t. Nhng kh&ocirc;ng hy b hoc thay i m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; s tha thun vi o&agrave;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ph thu ph&ograve;ng n: Trng hp kh&aacute;ch l i 1 m&agrave; ko ng gh&eacute;p o&agrave;n c hoc kh&aacute;ch mun  ri&ecirc;ng 1 ph&ograve;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Trong nhng trng hp kh&aacute;ch quan nh: khng b, thi&ecirc;n tai&hellip;hoc do c&oacute; s c, c&oacute; s thay i lch tr&igrave;nh ca c&aacute;c phng tin vn chuyn c&ocirc;ng cng nh: m&aacute;y bay, t&agrave;u ha&hellip;th&igrave; Cty s gi quyn thay i l tr&igrave;nh bt c l&uacute;c n&agrave;o v&igrave; s thun tin, an to&agrave;n cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; s kh&ocirc;ng chu tr&aacute;ch nhim bi thng nhng thit hi ph&aacute;t sinh**.</p>', 4, '19:54:00', '2021-01-22', '2021-01-26', ' T', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605945373187.gif', 0, 0, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:56:13', '2020-11-21 00:56:13'),
(8, 'faIvCuDvxz', 15, 'Tour  Nng 3N2D: Sn Tr - B N - Ng Hnh Sn - Hi An (Du Xun)', 'Sn Tr', 'Hi An', 2, 3490000, 2490000, 1490000, '<h3>Vui th&uacute; &agrave; th&agrave;nh mn m&ecirc; qu&ecirc;n li v</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&agrave; Nng l&agrave; mt trong 20 th&agrave;nh ph sch nht th gii. Nm  v&ugrave;ng Nam Trung B, &agrave; Nng c&oacute; c n&uacute;i, ng bng v&agrave; bin. C&aacute;c im tham quan du lch ni ting khi du lch &agrave; Nng bao gm khu du lch B&agrave; N&agrave;, b&atilde;i bin M Kh&ecirc;, v&agrave; khu vui chi gii tr&iacute; trong nh&agrave; Fantasy Park ln nht ch&acirc;u &Aacute;. &agrave; Nng c&ograve;n c&oacute; nhiu thng cnh m&ecirc; hn nh &egrave;o Hi V&acirc;n, rng nguy&ecirc;n sinh  b&aacute;n o Sn Tr&agrave; v&agrave; Ng H&agrave;nh Sn. C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; &agrave; Nng theo c&aacute;ch ri&ecirc;ng ca m&igrave;nh ngay h&ocirc;m nay!!!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>&nbsp;i qua nhng im tham quan g&acirc;y thng nh cho du kh&aacute;ch:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Thng ngon to&agrave;n cnh ph bin&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan B&aacute;n<strong>&nbsp;o Sn Tr&agrave;, Ving Linh ng T</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tn b ngm ph c&nbsp;<strong>Hi An</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham quan l&agrave;ng i&ecirc;u khc,&nbsp;<strong>Ng H&agrave;nh Sn</strong>.</p>', '<h3>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp;01: H CH&Iacute; MINH&nbsp;- &Agrave; NNG - SN TR&Agrave;&nbsp;- HI AN ( N TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng 05:00: Hng dn vi&ecirc;n &oacute;n v&agrave; l&agrave;m th tc &aacute;p chuyn bay i &agrave; Nng ti&nbsp;<strong>ga quc ni s&acirc;n bay T&acirc;n Sn Nht.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>08:00: Xe &amp; Hng Dn Vi&ecirc;n &oacute;n o&agrave;n ti s&acirc;n bay &agrave; Nng. Khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>B&aacute;n o Sn Tr&agrave; (Monkey Mountain)</strong>&nbsp;v&ograve;ng quanh B&aacute;n o  thng ngon to&agrave;n cnh ph bin &agrave; Nng tr&ecirc;n cao. Xe a qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch dc theo trin n&uacute;i &ocirc;ng Nam  chi&ecirc;m ngng v p tuyt m ca bin &agrave; Nng, ving&nbsp;<strong>Linh ng T</strong>&nbsp;- ni c&oacute; tng Pht B&agrave; 65m cao nht Vit Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/09/20/10/ivivu-chua-linh-ung.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch&ugrave;a Linh ng.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tra: Xe a o&agrave;n i d&ugrave;ng ba tra vi c sn ni ting &agrave; Nng &ldquo;B&aacute;nh tr&aacute;ng tht heo 2 u da &amp; M Qung&rdquo;. Xe a o&agrave;n v kh&aacute;ch sn nhn ph&ograve;ng ngh ngi. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tip tc: Xe a o&agrave;n v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>Ph c Hi An</strong>&nbsp;(Tnh Qung Nam), Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch tip tc h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh tham quan Ph c vi c&aacute;c di t&iacute;ch c k&iacute;nh nh:&nbsp;<strong>ch&ugrave;a cu Nht Bn, hi qu&aacute;n Phc Kin, nh&agrave; c Ph&ugrave;ng Hng.</strong>&nbsp;Sau ba cm chiu, o&agrave;n t do do ph thng ngon Hi An v &ecirc;m lung linh trong mu&ocirc;n sc &egrave;n lng, tham gia nhiu chng tr&igrave;nh ngh thut d&acirc;n gian truyn thng v&agrave; thng thc nhng m&oacute;n c sn d&acirc;n d&atilde; m cht a phng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/09/20/10/ivivu-chua-cau-hoi-an.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ph C Hi An.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ngi thuyn tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n (Chi ph&iacute; t t&uacute;c) ngm th&agrave;nh ph &agrave; Nng lung linh v &ecirc;m vi h&agrave;ng lot c&acirc;y Cu c &aacute;o v&agrave; ni ting hoc xem cu Rng phun La v&agrave; Nc (Th by hoc ch nht h&agrave;ng tun).</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp;02:&nbsp;KH&Aacute;M PH&Aacute; &Agrave; NNG&nbsp;( N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: Sau ba im t&acirc;m, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch i tham quan L&agrave;ng i&ecirc;u khc &aacute;&nbsp;<strong>Non Nc</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/27/09/ivivu-lang-da-my-nghe-non-nuoc.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>L&agrave;ng i&ecirc;u Khc &agrave; Non Nc.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &oacute; di chuyn qua&nbsp;<strong>Ng H&agrave;nh Sn</strong>, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch chi&ecirc;m b&aacute;i c&aacute;c danh lam v&agrave; thng ngon c&aacute;c thng cnh ni ting ni &acirc;y nh ch&ugrave;a Linh ng, Tam Thai, Non Nc; c&aacute;c ng nh: T&agrave;ng Chn, Huyn Kh&ocirc;ng, Hoa Nghi&ecirc;m; ng tr&ecirc;n Vng Giang &agrave;i hoc Vng Hi &agrave;i ngm nh&igrave;n to&agrave;n cnh n&uacute;i s&ocirc;ng tr&ugrave;ng ip v&agrave; bin c bao la...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/12/26/11/ivivu-ngu-hanh-son.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ng H&agrave;nh Sn.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tip Tc: Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th tham gia th&ecirc;m tour m</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LA CHN 1</strong>: Khi h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o Hi An ngi t&agrave;u Cao Tc ti bin Ca i i tham quan&nbsp;<strong>C&ugrave; Lao Ch&agrave;m</strong>&nbsp;(T t&uacute;c chi ph&iacute;, gi&aacute; tham kho 550.000/kh&aacute;ch), khu d tr sinh quyn Th gii gm cm o ngo&agrave;i khi bin &ocirc;ng c&aacute;ch Hi An 12 hi l&yacute;. Tham quan ch&ugrave;a Hi Tng hn 400 nm tui, &Acirc;u thuyn &ndash; khu vc tr&aacute;nh b&atilde;o ca ng d&acirc;n, Khu d&acirc;n c &amp; c&aacute;c lng miu c. (Nu Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch i v&agrave;o nhng ng&agrave;y c&oacute; ma, b&atilde;o, C&ocirc;ng ty s thay th bng nhng option b&ecirc;n di)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2020/05/08/09/ivivu-cu-lao-cham2.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>C&ugrave; Lao Ch&agrave;m.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LA CHN 2</strong>: Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch khi h&agrave;nh n C&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Sui kho&aacute;ng n&oacute;ng&nbsp;<strong>N&uacute;i Thn T&agrave;i</strong>&nbsp; kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; nhng li &iacute;ch ca sui kho&aacute;ng n&oacute;ng, th gi&atilde;n c th sau nhng thi gian cng thng v&agrave; mt mi (T t&uacute;c chi ph&iacute;, gi&aacute; tham kho 550.000/ kh&aacute;ch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2019/11/26/09/ivivu-nui-than-tai.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>N&uacute;i Thn T&agrave;i.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng tham gia tour m, th&igrave; Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th t do ti kh&aacute;ch sn v&agrave; tm bin/h bi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tra: o&agrave;n d&ugrave;ng ba tra v&agrave; t do tm bin, h bi kh&aacute;ch sn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: Xe &oacute;n o&agrave;n tham quan 1 v&ograve;ng th&agrave;nh ph&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti: Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng ba ti ti Nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng a phng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th t do do quanh th&agrave;nh ph&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>, chi&ecirc;m ngng v p&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>&nbsp;t tr&ecirc;n cao khi tham quan V&ograve;ng Quay Mt Tri (Chi ph&iacute; t t&uacute;c).</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp;03: &Agrave; NNG&nbsp;- B&Agrave; N&Agrave;&nbsp;- H CH&Iacute; MINH ( N S&Aacute;NG)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng: D&ugrave;ng im t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng ti kh&aacute;ch sn t do tm bin ti b&atilde;i bin M Kh&ecirc; v&agrave; mua sm n 10:00 Q&uacute;y Kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th tham gia tour m l&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; N&agrave;</strong>, thi&ecirc;n ng ngh dng min Trung vi nhiu thng cnh, dch v vui chi v&agrave; gii tr&iacute; hp dn (T t&uacute;c chi ph&iacute; v&eacute; 860.000 bao gm v&eacute; C&aacute;p Treo B&agrave; N&agrave; v&agrave; ba n tra di ch&acirc;n n&uacute;i). Ni m&agrave; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; nhng khonh khc giao m&ugrave;a bt ng Xu&acirc;n &ndash; H - Thu &ndash; &ocirc;ng trong 1 ng&agrave;y.&nbsp; Ngi c&aacute;p treo d&agrave;i nht th gii (gn 6.000m), tham quan&nbsp;<strong>i Vng Nguyt, ch&ugrave;a Linh ng, Th&iacute;ch Ca Pht &agrave;i, c&acirc;y Cu V&agrave;ng B&agrave; N&agrave;</strong>&nbsp;thu h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng triu lt du kh&aacute;ch n &acirc;y tham quan, khu chung nga c ca Ph&aacute;p, vn tnh t&acirc;m v&agrave; nh nh&agrave; r&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/12/06/17/ivivu-cau-vang-ba-na.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Cu V&agrave;ng B&agrave; N&agrave; Hills.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tra: Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch t t&uacute;c d&ugrave;ng ba tra vi c sn &agrave; Nng. Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch l&agrave;m th tc tr ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chiu: 14:30 Hng dn vi&ecirc;n tin kh&aacute;ch s&acirc;n bay &agrave; Nng &aacute;p chuyn bay v li TP. H Ch&iacute; Minh. Kt th&uacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh, chia tay v&agrave; hn gp li Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch trong c&aacute;c chuyn trong trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nc.</p>', '<p>- Tr em t 02 tui n di 05 tui: gi&aacute; tour theo khung gi&aacute; b&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n (02 v chng c k&egrave;m theo 1 tr, tr Em th 2 cn mua theo xut ngi ln  m bo ch ng ph&ugrave; hp). Ti&ecirc;u chun tr em c&oacute; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay, gh ngi tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng chung vi Cha M. C&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; n ung tham quan c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh gia &igrave;nh t lo cho Em.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tr em t 05 tui n di 11 tui: gi&aacute; tour theo khung gi&aacute; b&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n (02 v chng c k&egrave;m theo 1 tr, tr Em th 2 cn mua theo xut ngi ln  m bo ch ng ph&ugrave; hp). Ti&ecirc;u chun tr em c&oacute; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay, gh ngi tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng chung vi Cha M.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Em b&eacute; di 02 tui: 500.000 VN/B&Eacute; bao gm c&oacute; thu ph&iacute; h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, bo him (Kh&ocirc;ng bao gm gh ngi tr&ecirc;n xe, Ph thu th&ecirc;m 300.000 VN nu mua th&ecirc;m sut gh ngi, nhng phi ng k&yacute; ngay khi ng k&yacute; tour) nhng 2 v chng ch c k&egrave;m 01 em b&eacute; di 02 tui, nu b&eacute; th 02 t&iacute;nh gi&aacute; tr em theo khung t 2 n di 5 tui.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- T 11 tui tr l&ecirc;n c xem nh ngi ln.</p>', 3, '18:57:00', '2021-01-15', '2021-01-18', ' t', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605945540119.gif', 10, 0, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 00:59:00', '2020-11-21 00:59:00'),
(9, 'jUO28zfaiG', 20, 'Tour  Nng 4N3D: Sn Tr - Hi An - B N (Cu Vng) - Hu', 'Sn Tr', 'Hi An - B N (Cu Vng) - Hu', 10, 2550000, 1550000, 1000000, '<h3>Chinh phc cung ng di sn min Trung</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Min Trung, di t th&acirc;n thng ni lin hai min Nam - Bc ca Vit Nam. &ldquo;Cung ng di sn min Trung&rdquo; s kt ni du kh&aacute;ch vi c&aacute;c di sn vn h&oacute;a ca nh&acirc;n loi c UNESCO c&ocirc;ng nhn bao gm: Hu vi hai di sn l&agrave; Qun th di t&iacute;ch C &ocirc; Hu v&agrave; Nh&atilde; Nhc cung &igrave;nh; Qung Nam vi hai di sn l&agrave; Th&aacute;nh a M Sn v&agrave; &ocirc; th c Hi An. Tr&ecirc;n mi bc i, du kh&aacute;ch c&ograve;n c&oacute; th kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; cho m&igrave;nh nhiu im n hp dn: B&agrave; N&agrave; Hill, L&agrave;ng Ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;, v&agrave; nhiu b&atilde;i tm tuyt p: Ca i, Non Nc, Lng C&ocirc;, Nht L, c&ugrave;ng vi nhng n&eacute;t m thc c &aacute;o ca Min Trung. C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; cung ng tuyt vi n&agrave;y ngay h&ocirc;m nay!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>t o&agrave;n ri&ecirc;ng li&ecirc;n h 028 3933 8002 hoc hotline 0906 355 542  c&oacute; gi&aacute; tt </strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Du kh&aacute;ch s kh&ocirc;ng ngng thn thc bi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Hi An&nbsp;vi&nbsp;Ch&ugrave;a Cu Nht Bn,&nbsp;Nh&agrave; C&nbsp;h&agrave;ng trm nm tui,&nbsp;Hi Qu&aacute;n Phc Kin&nbsp;&amp; Xng th c&ocirc;ng m ngh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Lu li nhng bc nh  i &nbsp;cu B&agrave;n Tay V&agrave;ng&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;B&agrave; N&agrave; Hills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Thng thc&nbsp;Ca Hu tr&ecirc;n S&ocirc;ng Hng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;&nbsp;i Ni Hu&nbsp;vi nhng kin tr&uacute;c c &aacute;o c&ograve;n li thi nh&agrave; Nguyn.</p>', '<h3>Chng tr&igrave;nh tour</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>KHUYN M&Atilde;I &Aacute;P DNG T&nbsp;16/05/2020 &ndash; 15/07/2020.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tng v&eacute; Du thuyn S&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n vi c&aacute;c dch v ca m&uacute;a nhc hp dn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tng v&eacute; Buffet tra ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng 4 sao Banahills vi menu m thc 3 min hp dn v&agrave; phong ph&uacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 01: &Oacute;N KH&Aacute;CH &ndash; SN TR&Agrave; - &Agrave; NNG (N TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;&oacute;n qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ti&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng</strong>&nbsp;(S&acirc;n bay, Ga, im hn trung t&acirc;m) t 07h00 n 13h00 (Sau thi gian n&agrave;y, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t t&uacute;c nhp o&agrave;n). Xe a i n tra c sn ni ting &agrave; Nng &ldquo;<strong>B&aacute;nh tr&aacute;ng tht heo 2 u da &amp; M Qung</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/08/23/15/ivivu-banh-trang-thit-heo-2-dau-da.jpg\" style=\"height:398px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<em>B&aacute;nh Tr&aacute;ng Tht Heo.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhn ph&ograve;ng K/sn 3* ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp; Khi h&agrave;nh n&nbsp;<strong>B&aacute;n o Sn Tr&agrave;</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Rng gi&agrave; gia l&ograve;ng ph tr ving&nbsp;<strong>Linh ng T</strong>&nbsp;- ni c&oacute; tng Pht B&agrave; 67m hng ra bin &ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/09/20/10/ivivu-chua-linh-ung.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ch&ugrave;a Linh ng Sn Tr&agrave;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &oacute; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t t&uacute;c tri nghim h&agrave;ng lot tr&ograve; chi hin i, cm gi&aacute;c mnh h&agrave;ng u&nbsp;<strong>&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute;</strong>&nbsp;ti&nbsp;<strong>Sunworld Danang Wonders - C&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Ch&acirc;u &Aacute;</strong>&nbsp;(chi ph&iacute; t t&uacute;c).</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 02:&nbsp;BO T&Agrave;NG PHT HC &ndash; PH C HI AN (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;im t&acirc;m. V&ograve;ng qua&nbsp;<strong>Cu Rng</strong>&nbsp;lu li du n tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Cu T&igrave;nh Y&ecirc;u</strong>, tn b thng thc kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; trong l&agrave;nh b&ecirc;n b H&agrave;n Giang vi tng&nbsp;<strong>C&aacute; Ch&eacute;p H&oacute;a Long</strong>&nbsp;- Biu tng mong mun vn l&ecirc;n ca ngi &agrave; Nng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/09/20/10/ivivu-cau-rong.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Cu Rng.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Quan Th &Acirc;m</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;Bo T&agrave;ng Pht Hc</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>L&agrave;ng Ngh i&ecirc;u Khc &aacute;</strong>. Mua sm c sn Qu&agrave; Min Trung.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp; Khi h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>Hi An</strong>&nbsp;b&aacute;ch b tham quan v&agrave; mua sm Ph C vi:&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Cu Nht Bn, Nh&agrave; C h&agrave;ng trm nm tui, Hi Qu&aacute;n Phc Kin</strong>&nbsp;&amp; Xng th c&ocirc;ng m ngh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/06/22/14/ivivu-pho-co-hoi-an.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<em>Hi An.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi h&agrave;nh v li&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Nng.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng. T do thng ngon du thuyn tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n ngm cnh &agrave; Th&agrave;nh v &ecirc;m, chp nh&nbsp;<strong>Cu Quay S&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n</strong>, cu&nbsp;<strong>Rng phun la</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; nc v&agrave;o cui tun.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 03: B&Agrave; N&Agrave; - C &Ocirc; HU (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>im t&acirc;m. Khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; N&agrave; - N&uacute;i Ch&uacute;</strong>a.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s tn hng cm gi&aacute;c bng bn khi ngi tr&ecirc;n Cabin l lng gia chng m&acirc;y.&nbsp;<strong>Ving ch&ugrave;a Linh ng</strong>&nbsp;vi tng Pht Th&iacute;ch Ca cao 27m, ving n th&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; Ch&uacute;a Mu Thng Ng&agrave;n.</strong>&nbsp;Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Cu v&agrave;ng - HOT</strong>&nbsp;C&acirc;y cu c &aacute;o nm trong vn Thi&ecirc;n Thai  B&agrave; N&agrave; Hill - c x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n  cao 1.400m so vi mt nc bin, c&acirc;y cu gm 8 nhp v&agrave; c&oacute;  d&agrave;i l&agrave; 150m. C&acirc;y cu c n&acirc;ng  bi &ocirc;i b&agrave;n tay khng l. Ngi i nh lc gia ti&ecirc;n cnh ni c&oacute; m&acirc;y, tri bao la. (V&eacute; c&aacute;p treo B&agrave; N&agrave; t t&uacute;c)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tham gia vui chi ti&nbsp;<strong>c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Fantasy Park</strong>: vi c&aacute;c tr&ograve; chi phi&ecirc;u lu mi l nh: V&ograve;ng Quay T&igrave;nh Y&ecirc;u, Phi C&ocirc;ng Skiver, ng ua La, Ng&ocirc;i Nh&agrave; Ma v&agrave; Khu trng b&agrave;y hn 40 tng s&aacute;p nhng nh&acirc;n vt ni ting tr&ecirc;n th gii&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/06/22/14/ivivu-ba-na-nui-chua.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>B&agrave; N&agrave; Hills.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>C &ocirc; Hu - Di sn vn ho&aacute; Th Gii</strong>, xuy&ecirc;n hm ng b &egrave;o Hi v&acirc;n, dng ch&acirc;n chp nh l&agrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>Ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/12/06/17/ivivu-lang-chai-lang-co.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:710px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>L&agrave;ng Ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhn ph&ograve;ng K/sn 4* ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng vi c sn x Hu (B&aacute;nh b&egrave;o, lc, nm, kho&aacute;i,...). Ngi thuyn Rng nghe&nbsp;<strong>Ca Hu</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; th hoa ng cu may tr&ecirc;n d&ograve;ng Hng Giang th mng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 04:&nbsp;LNG KHI NH - I NI &ndash; CH&Ugrave;A THI&Ecirc;N M - TIN KH&Aacute;CH (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;im t&acirc;m. im t&acirc;m. Khi h&agrave;nh tham quan tham quan&nbsp;<strong>i Ni - Ho&agrave;ng Cung</strong>&nbsp;ca 13 v vua triu Nguyn, triu i phong kin cui c&ugrave;ng ca Vit Nam v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Thi&ecirc;n M</strong>&nbsp;c k&iacute;nh. o&agrave;n tip tc di chuyn n tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Lng Khi nh</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh lng c&oacute; c s kt hp tuyt vi ca kin tr&uacute;c &ocirc;ng - T&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/05/14/17/ivivu-dai-noi-hue.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>i Ni Ho&agrave;ng Cung.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng ti<strong>&nbsp;Hu.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Tin Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ti&nbsp;<strong>s&acirc;n bay Hu</strong>&nbsp;(c&aacute;c chuyn bay sau 17:00).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi h&agrave;nh v &agrave; Nng, tm bin&nbsp;<strong>M Kh&ecirc;</strong>. Tin qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ra s&acirc;n bay &agrave; Nng (c&aacute;c chuyn bay sau 19:00).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kt th&uacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh. Hn gp li Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch!</p>', '<p>-&nbsp;Tr&igrave;nh t chng tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; th thay i nhng s lng chng tr&igrave;nh vn kh&ocirc;ng thay i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; mt ti im &oacute;n trc 15 ph&uacute;t. Du kh&aacute;ch n tr khi xe &atilde; khi h&agrave;nh hoc hy tour kh&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trc vui l&ograve;ng chu ph&iacute; nh &lsquo;hy v&eacute; ngay ng&agrave;y khi h&agrave;nh&rsquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mang theo giy CMND hoc H chiu (Bn ch&iacute;nh), n&ecirc;n mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; gn nh, kh&ocirc;ng mang valy ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Tr em phi i c&ugrave;ng cha m hoc c&oacute; giy cam kt i tour c&ugrave;ng ngi th&acirc;n, khi i phi mang theo giy khai sinh hoc h chiu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t qun l&yacute; tin bc t trang trong qua tr&igrave;nh tham quan du lch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Khi ng k&yacute;, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng cung cp y  H t&ecirc;n v&agrave; nm sinh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;i vi du kh&aacute;ch l&agrave; Vit kiu, Quc t nhp cnh Vit Nam bng visa ri, vui l&ograve;ng mang theo t khai hi quan v&agrave; visa khi i tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Chng tr&igrave;nh tour c coi l&agrave; bi&ecirc;n bn ghi nh gia kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; Ivivu. Nhng thc mc, khiu ni s da v&agrave;o nhng quy nh trong chng tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; phiu thu  gii quyt.</p>', 4, '18:00:00', '2021-01-24', '2021-01-28', ' t', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605945744949.jpg', 15, 0, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 01:02:24', '2020-11-21 01:02:24');
