(10, 'cTYbXOuovU', 25, 'Tour  Nng 4N3D: Hi An - B N - Hu', 'Hi An', 'Hu', 10, 3050000, 1050000, 1000000, '<h3>Chinh phc cung ng di sn min Trung</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Min Trung, di t th&acirc;n thng ni lin hai min Nam - Bc ca Vit Nam. &ldquo;Cung ng di sn min Trung&rdquo; s kt ni du kh&aacute;ch vi c&aacute;c di sn vn h&oacute;a ca nh&acirc;n loi c UNESCO c&ocirc;ng nhn bao gm: Qung B&igrave;nh c&ugrave;ng Vn quc gia Phong Nha - K B&agrave;ng; Hu vi hai di sn l&agrave; Qun th di t&iacute;ch C &ocirc; Hu v&agrave; Nh&atilde; Nhc cung &igrave;nh; Qung Nam vi hai di sn l&agrave; Th&aacute;nh a M Sn v&agrave; &ocirc; th c Hi An. Tr&ecirc;n mi bc i, du kh&aacute;ch c&ograve;n c&oacute; th kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; cho m&igrave;nh nhiu im n hp dn: B&agrave; N&agrave; Hill, L&agrave;ng Ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;, v&agrave; nhiu b&atilde;i tm tuyt p: Ca i, Non Nc, Lng C&ocirc;, Nht L, c&ugrave;ng vi nhng n&eacute;t m thc c &aacute;o ca Min Trung. C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; cung ng tuyt vi n&agrave;y ngay h&ocirc;m nay!<br />\r\n<em><strong>t o&agrave;n ri&ecirc;ng li&ecirc;n h 028 3933 8002 hoc hotline 0906 355 542  c&oacute; gi&aacute; tt </strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Du kh&aacute;ch s kh&ocirc;ng ngng thn thc bi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Hi An</strong>&nbsp;vi&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Cu Nht Bn,&nbsp;Nh&agrave; C&nbsp;h&agrave;ng trm nm tui,&nbsp;Hi Qu&aacute;n Phc Kin</strong>&nbsp;&amp; Xng th c&ocirc;ng m ngh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Lu li nhng bc nh  i &nbsp;<strong>cu B&agrave;n Tay V&agrave;ng</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; N&agrave; Hills</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Thng thc&nbsp;<strong>Ca Hu tr&ecirc;n S&ocirc;ng Hng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>ng Thi&ecirc;n ng:</strong>&nbsp;Ho&agrave;ng cung l&ograve;ng t s hu k quan tr&aacute;ng l v&agrave; huyn o bc nht th gii.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;&nbsp;<strong>i Ni Hu</strong>&nbsp;vi nhng kin tr&uacute;c c &aacute;o c&ograve;n li thi nh&agrave; Nguyn.</p>', '<h3>Chng tr&igrave;nh tour</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>KHUYN M&Atilde;I &Aacute;P DNG T&nbsp;16/05/2020 &ndash; 15/07/2020.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tng v&eacute; Du thuyn S&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n vi c&aacute;c dch v ca m&uacute;a nhc hp dn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tng v&eacute; Buffet tra ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng 4 sao Banahills vi menu m thc 3 min hp dn v&agrave; phong ph&uacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 1: BO T&Agrave;NG PHT HC &Agrave; NNG &ndash; HI AN (N TRA, TI)&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;&oacute;n kh&aacute;ch ti &agrave; Nng t 7h00 &ndash; 09h00 (s&acirc;n bay/ga /im hn). V&ograve;ng qua&nbsp;<strong>Cu Rng</strong>&nbsp;lu li du n tr&ecirc;n Cu T&igrave;nh Y&ecirc;u, tn b thng thc kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; trong l&agrave;nh b&ecirc;n&nbsp; b &nbsp;H&agrave;n Giang vi tng&nbsp;<strong>C&aacute; Ch&eacute;p H&oacute;a Long</strong>&nbsp;- Biu tng mong mun vn l&ecirc;n ca ngi &agrave; Nng. Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Quan Th &Acirc;m - &nbsp;Bo T&agrave;ng Pht Hc v&agrave; L&agrave;ng Ngh i&ecirc;u Khc &aacute;</strong>. Mua sm c sn Q&ugrave;a Min Trung.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/08/23/15/ivivu-cau-tinh-yeu.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Cu T&igrave;nh Y&ecirc;u &agrave; Nng.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Khi h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o Hi An b&aacute;ch b tham quan v&agrave; mua sm&nbsp;<strong>Ph C</strong>&nbsp;vi:&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Cu Nht Bn</strong>,<strong>&nbsp;Nh&agrave; C</strong>&nbsp;h&agrave;ng trm nm tui,&nbsp;<strong>Hi Qu&aacute;n Phc Kin &amp; Xng th c&ocirc;ng m ngh</strong>. Khi h&agrave;nh v li &agrave; Nng</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng. T do thng ngon du thuyn tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>s&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n</strong>&nbsp;ngm cnh&nbsp;<strong>&agrave; Th&agrave;nh</strong>&nbsp;v &ecirc;m, chp nh&nbsp;<strong>Cu Quay S&ocirc;ng H&agrave;n</strong>, cu Rng phun la v&agrave; nc v&agrave;o cui tun.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 2: B&Agrave; N&Agrave; (CU V&Agrave;NG) - C &Ocirc; HU (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;im t&acirc;m. Khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; N&agrave; - N&uacute;i Ch&uacute;a</strong>. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s tn hng cm gi&aacute;c bng bn khi ngi tr&ecirc;n Cabin l lng gia chng m&acirc;y. Ving&nbsp;<strong>ch&ugrave;a Linh ng</strong>&nbsp;vi tng Pht Th&iacute;ch Ca cao 27m, ving n th&nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; Ch&uacute;a Mu Thng Ng&agrave;n</strong>. Tham quan&nbsp;<strong>Cu v&agrave;ng - HOT</strong>&nbsp;C&acirc;y cu c &aacute;o nm trong vn Thi&ecirc;n Thai &nbsp;<strong>B&agrave; N&agrave; Hill</strong>&nbsp;- c x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n  cao 1.400m so vi mt nc bin, c&acirc;y cu gm 8 nhp v&agrave; c&oacute;  d&agrave;i l&agrave; 150m. C&acirc;y cu c n&acirc;ng  bi &ocirc;i b&agrave;n tay khng l. Ngi i nh lc gia ti&ecirc;n cnh ni c&oacute; m&acirc;y, tri bao la. (V&eacute; c&aacute;p treo B&agrave; N&agrave; t t&uacute;c).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/12/06/17/ivivu-cau-vang-ba-na.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Cu B&agrave;n Tay B&agrave; N&agrave; Hills.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tham gia vui chi ti c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Fantasy Park: vi c&aacute;c tr&ograve; chi phi&ecirc;u lu mi l nh: V&ograve;ng Quay T&igrave;nh Y&ecirc;u, Phi C&ocirc;ng Skiver, ng ua La, Ng&ocirc;i Nh&agrave; Ma v&agrave; Khu trng b&agrave;y hn 40 tng s&aacute;p nhng nh&acirc;n vt ni ting tr&ecirc;n th gii&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Khi h&agrave;nh i&nbsp;<strong>C &ocirc; Hu</strong>&nbsp;- Di sn vn ho&aacute; Th Gii, xuy&ecirc;n hm ng b&nbsp;<strong>&egrave;o Hi V&acirc;n</strong>, dng ch&acirc;n ti&nbsp;<strong>l&agrave;ng ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;</strong>&nbsp;chp h&igrave;nh lu nim.&nbsp;Nhn ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn 4* ngh ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2018/12/06/17/ivivu-lang-co-beach.jpg\" style=\"height:400px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>L&agrave;ng Ch&agrave;i Lng C&ocirc;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng vi c sn x Hu (B&aacute;nh b&egrave;o, lc, nm, kho&aacute;i,...). Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch xu&ocirc;ng thuy&ecirc;n R&ocirc;ng &ecirc; thng thc&nbsp;<strong>Ca Hu&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng Hng</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; net vn hoa &ocirc;c ao cua x Hu&ecirc;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 3: HU - TH&Aacute;NH A LA VANG &ndash; NG PHONG NHA (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA, TI) &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;im t&acirc;m sm. Ri Hu i&nbsp;<strong>Phong Nha - K B&agrave;ng</strong>. Tr&ecirc;n ng, ving thm&nbsp;<strong>Th&aacute;nh a La Vang</strong>&nbsp;(c phong tng l&agrave; Tiu Vng Cung Th&aacute;nh ng) v&agrave; ngang qua&nbsp;<strong>V tuyn 17 S&ocirc;ng Bn Hi - Cu Hin Lng</strong>&nbsp;huy&ecirc;n thoai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/08/25/16/ivivu-tour-da-nang-3n2d-ba-na-hue-dong-phong-nha-thanh-dia-la-vang.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Th&aacute;nh a La Vang.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng ti Phong Nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Ngi thuyn ngc s&ocirc;ng Son chinh phc ng Phong Nha: C&ocirc; Ti&ecirc;n &amp; Cung &igrave;nh di s&acirc;u l&ograve;ng n&uacute;i ni c&oacute; con s&ocirc;ng ngm t L&agrave;o chy sang, chi&ecirc;m ngng c&aacute;c khi thch nh tuyt p c kin to bi thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n qua h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;n thi&ecirc;n ni&ecirc;n k. Khi h&agrave;nh v Hu theo ng Trng Sn - H Ch&iacute; Minh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Hoc:</em>&nbsp;la chn ngi xe in tham quan chinh phc ng Thi&ecirc;n ng - Ho&agrave;ng cung l&ograve;ng t s hu k quan tr&aacute;ng l v&agrave; huyn o bc nht th gii. Ph thu th&ecirc;m 100.000 vn/kh&aacute;ch ch&ecirc;nh lch v&eacute; tham quan).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2016/08/25/17/ivivu-tour-da-nang-4n3d-hoi-an-ba-na-hue-dong-phong-nha-dong-phong-nha.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>ng Thi&ecirc;n ng.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti:</strong>&nbsp;n ti nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, t do kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; C &ocirc; v &ecirc;m vi&nbsp;<strong>cu Tr&agrave;ng Tin</strong>&nbsp;rc r soi m&igrave;nh xung d&ograve;ng&nbsp;<strong>s&ocirc;ng Hng</strong>&nbsp;th mng, do chi ch &ecirc;m t&igrave;m hiu n&eacute;t sinh hot ca t kinh th&agrave;nh. Ngh kh&aacute;ch sn 4*.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 4:&nbsp;LNG KHI NH - I NI &ndash; CH&Ugrave;A THI&Ecirc;N M - TIN KH&Aacute;CH (N S&Aacute;NG, TRA)&nbsp; &nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong>&nbsp;im t&acirc;m.Khi h&agrave;nh tham quan&nbsp;<strong>i Ni - Ho&agrave;ng cung triu Nguyn</strong>, tham quan Ng M&ocirc;n, in Th&aacute;i H&ograve;a, T Cm Th&agrave;nh, Th Miu, Hin L&acirc;m C&aacute;c, Cu nh,...tip tc ving&nbsp;<strong>Ch&ugrave;a Thi&ecirc;n M</strong>&nbsp;c k&iacute;nh l&agrave; ni lu gi nhiu c vt qu&yacute; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr v mt lch s v&agrave; ngh thut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.ivivu.com/2017/09/22/14/tour-da-nang-4n3d-hoi-an-ba-na-hue-dong-phong-nha-hue.jpg\" style=\"height:399px; width:710px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>i Ni Hu.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>o&agrave;n tip tc di chuyn n tham quan Lng Khi nh &ndash; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh lng c&oacute; c s kt hp tuyt vi ca kin tr&uacute;c &ocirc;ng - T&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tra:</strong>&nbsp;n tra nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng ti Hu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chiu:</strong>&nbsp;Tin qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ra s&acirc;n bay Hu (c&aacute;c chuyn sau 17:00).V&agrave; s&acirc;n bay &agrave; Nng (c&aacute;c chuyn sau 19:00). Chia tay Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; kt th&uacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh. Hn gp li qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch!</p>', '<p>-&nbsp;Tr&igrave;nh t chng tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; th thay i nhng s lng chng tr&igrave;nh vn kh&ocirc;ng thay i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; mt ti im &oacute;n trc 15 ph&uacute;t. Du kh&aacute;ch n tr khi xe &atilde; khi h&agrave;nh hoc hy tour kh&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trc vui l&ograve;ng chu ph&iacute; nh &lsquo;hy v&eacute; ngay ng&agrave;y khi h&agrave;nh&rsquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mang theo giy CMND hoc H chiu (Bn ch&iacute;nh), n&ecirc;n mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; gn nh, kh&ocirc;ng mang valy ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Tr em phi i c&ugrave;ng cha m hoc c&oacute; giy cam kt i tour c&ugrave;ng ngi th&acirc;n, khi i phi mang theo giy khai sinh hoc h chiu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t qun l&yacute; tin bc t trang trong qua tr&igrave;nh tham quan du lch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Khi ng k&yacute;, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng cung cp y  H t&ecirc;n v&agrave; nm sinh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;i vi du kh&aacute;ch l&agrave; Vit kiu, Quc t nhp cnh Vit Nam bng visa ri, vui l&ograve;ng mang theo t khai hi quan v&agrave; visa khi i tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;Chng tr&igrave;nh tour c coi l&agrave; bi&ecirc;n bn ghi nh gia kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; Ivivu. Nhng thc mc, khiu ni s da v&agrave;o nhng quy nh trong chng tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; phiu thu  gii quyt.</p>', 4, '18:03:00', '2021-01-22', '2021-01-26', ' t', '2020-Nov-Sat_1605945914283.jpg', 14, 0, 0, '2', '2', '2020-11-21 01:05:14', '2020-11-21 01:05:14'),
(11, 'JBnxcnPmiL', 15, 'Tour Bun M Thut 3N3D: Gia Lai - Kon Tum - Mng en', ' Nng', 'Mng en', 1, 1888000, 1000000, 500000, '<h3>H&ugrave;ng v v&ugrave;ng t T&acirc;y Nguy&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>c xem l&agrave; trung t&acirc;m ca vn h&oacute;a T&acirc;y Nguy&ecirc;n, Bu&ocirc;n Ma Thut quyn r du kh&aacute;ch nh nhng c&aacute;nh ng c&agrave; ph&ecirc; bt ng&agrave;n, nhng con th&aacute;c cao ngt h&ugrave;ng v hay v p ca d&ograve;ng S&ecirc;r&ecirc;p&ocirc;k huyn thoi. H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; Bu&ocirc;n Ma Thut nu bn ang c&oacute; &yacute; nh du lch n &acirc;y nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>t o&agrave;n ri&ecirc;ng li&ecirc;n h 028 3933 8002 hoc hotline 0906 355 542  c&oacute; gi&aacute; tt </strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bu&ocirc;n M&ecirc; Thut ni bt l&ecirc;n gia T&acirc;y Nguy&ecirc;n bi...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Nh&agrave; Th G Kon Tum:&nbsp;</strong>thuc top 10 nh&agrave; th p ca Vit Nam, mt kit t&aacute;c bi c thit k theo kin tr&uacute;c Romantic, phi hp h&agrave;i ho&agrave; kiu nh&agrave; s&agrave;n ca ngi Ba Na n&ecirc;n m sc th&aacute;i vn h&oacute;a, t&iacute;n ngng ngi d&acirc;n cao nguy&ecirc;n t nhng ng n&eacute;t ha tit n nhng im nhn tr&ecirc;n cht liu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Khu Du lch Mng en:&nbsp;</strong>Rng nguy&ecirc;n sinh ph k&iacute;n khp ni, kh&iacute; hu m&aacute;t m quanh nm vi nhiu thng cnh h, th&aacute;c khin du kh&aacute;ch ng lc bc gia &#39;thi&ecirc;n ng ngh dng&#39; Mng en.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Thy in Yaly:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>th&aacute;c Yaly c bit n l&agrave; mt th&aacute;c nc p th&igrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh thu in Yaly  s bao gm p d&acirc;ng, p tr&agrave;n x l b&ecirc;n mt h nc trong b&aacute;t ng&aacute;t vi mt h rng hn 65km2 gia khung cnh thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n p n nao l&ograve;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<strong>Th&aacute;c Dray Nur:&nbsp;</strong>l&agrave; ngn th&aacute;c tuyt p thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n ban tn