(14, '9NIZuEBMBx', 10, 'Tour Du thuyn Victoria Mekong 3N2D: Khm Ph Cn Th - Chu c', ' Nng', 'An Giang', 2, 3000000, 0, 200000, '<h3>Du thuyn Victoria Mekong - Gn Gi Vi S&ocirc;ng Nc Min T&acirc;y</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Cuc sng thng nht ti ng bng s&ocirc;ng Cu Long tp trung ch yu tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng nc: nhng khu nha s&agrave;n ni tr&ecirc;n nc, khu ch ni tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng... hng ng&agrave;y lu&ocirc;n nhn nhp ngi d&acirc;n bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n, &aacute;nh bt, sinh hot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt c c&aacute;c du thuy&ecirc;n Victoria u c thi&ecirc;t k&ecirc; theo phong c&aacute;ch gn gi nht vi thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n, vi c&aacute;c cht liu t m&acirc;y, tre v&agrave; g&ocirc; chuy&ecirc;n dng, l&agrave; phng tin l&yacute; tng cho chuyn du lch kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; s&ocirc;ng nc ti Mekong ca du kh&aacute;ch. H thng du thuyn ca Victoria phc v nhiu tour phong phu, tham quan nhiu im n ni ting ti min T&acirc;y. C&ugrave;ng iVIVU kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; ngay h&ocirc;m nay!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nhng tri nghim th&uacute; v trong chng tr&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Du thuyn<strong>&nbsp;Victoria Mekong</strong>&nbsp;4 sao &atilde; sn s&agrave;ng cho h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh ngc d&ograve;ng M&ecirc; K&ocirc;ng t&nbsp;<strong>Cn Th - Long Xuy&ecirc;n - Cn Th</strong>&nbsp;vi c&aacute;c im ni bt c&oacute; trong chng tr&igrave;nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Thng thc&nbsp;<strong>cocktail</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; ngm ho&agrave;ng h&ocirc;n tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Biu din &acirc;m nhc d&acirc;n gian &ldquo;n Ca T&agrave;i T&rdquo;.</p>', '<h3>NG&Agrave;Y 1: CN TH &ndash; LONG XUY&Ecirc;N ( N TI)&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Du thuyn&nbsp;<strong>Victoria Mekong</strong>&nbsp;&oacute;n kh&aacute;ch ti cng C&aacute;i Cui (Cn Th) l&uacute;c 3:00 chiu. Khi t&agrave;u khi h&agrave;nh, h&atilde;y bt u t&igrave;m hiu c&aacute;c dch v ca du thuyn v&agrave; nh&acirc;m nhi ly cocktail ti m&aacute;t di &aacute;nh ho&agrave;ng h&ocirc;n tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng Hu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn2.